590856,122,1595,2,4,1,23,2,4 . Mahākappinattheravatthu 
590857,122,1596,2,15,1,104,11,Dhammapīti sukhaṃ {setī}ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto mahākappinattheraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
590858,122,1597,2,22,1,188,19,Tatrāyaṃ anupubbī kathā– atīte kira āyasmā mahākappino padumuttarabuddhassa pādamūle katābhinīhāro saṃsāre saṃsaranto bārāṇasito avidūre ekasmiṃ pesakāragāme jeṭṭhakapesakāro hutvā nibbatti. 
590859,122,1597,23,35,1,98,12,Tadā sahassamattā paccekabuddhā aṭṭha māse himavante vasitvā vassike cattāro māse janapade vasanti. 
590860,122,1597,36,55,1,129,14,Te ekavāraṃ bārāṇasiyā avidūre otaritvā‘‘ senāsanakaraṇatthāya hatthakammaṃ yācathā’’ ti rañño santikaṃ aṭṭha paccekabuddhe pahiṇiṃsu. 
590861,122,1597,56,61,1,37,5,Tadā pana rañño vappamaṅgalakālo hoti. 
590862,122,1597,62,99,1,202,25,"So‘‘ paccekabuddhā kira āgatā’’ ti sutvā tasmiṃ khaṇe nikkhamitvā āgatakāraṇaṃ pucchitvā‘‘ ajja, bhante, okāso natthi, sve amhākaṃ vappamaṅgalaṃ, tatiyadivase karissāmī’’ ti vatvā paccekabuddhe animantetvāva pāvisi. "
590863,122,1597,100,109,1,46,5,Paccekabuddhā‘‘ aññattha gamissāmā’’ ti pakkamiṃsu. 
590864,122,1597,110,140,1,179,22,"Tasmiṃ khaṇe jeṭṭhapesakārassa bhariyā kenacideva karaṇīyena bārāṇasiṃ gacchantī te paccekabuddhe disvā vanditvā‘‘ kiṃ, bhante, avelāya, ayyā, āgatā’’ ti pucchitvā ādito paṭṭhāya kathesuṃ. "
590865,122,1597,141,160,1,102,13,"Taṃ pavattiṃ sutvā saddhāsampannā ñāṇasampannā itthī‘‘ sve, bhante, amhākaṃ bhikkhaṃ gaṇhathā’’ ti nimantesi."
