591041,122,1617,27,35,1,67,6,"So nibbattanibbattaṭṭhāne bhogasampadaṃ labhati, no parivārasampadaṃ. "
591042,122,1617,36,43,1,38,6,"Ekacco paraṃ samādapeti, attanā na deti. "
