591095,122,1621,76,96,1,125,16,So antarāpaṇe paṇṇaṃ adisvā nadītīraṃ gantvā‘‘ ajja ayyānaṃ bhojanaṃ dātuṃ labhissāmī’’ ti pahaṭṭhamānaso gāyanto paṇṇaṃ uccinati. 
591096,122,1621,97,113,1,92,11,Mahājālaṃ khipitvā ṭhito kevaṭṭo ‘‘ mahāduggatassa saddena bhavitabban’’ ti taṃ pakkositvā pucchi–
