591122,122,1622,236,255,1,80,13,"‘‘ Samma, mayaṃ tava kammena atthikā, tuyhaṃ pana kiñci dātabbaṃ bhatiṃ na passāmā’’ ti."
591123,122,1622,256,265,1,24,5,‘‘ Kiṃ pana te kattabban’’ ti?
