591128,122,1622,334,342,1,75,8,Dānaveyyāvaṭikopi paṇṇe āropitaniyāmeneva tesaṃ tesaṃ gehāni bhikkhū pahiṇi. 
591129,122,1623,2,15,1,66,9,Mahāduggato tassa santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ mayhaṃ pattabhikkhuṃ dehī’’ ti āha. 
591130,122,1623,16,31,1,65,11,So tasmiṃ khaṇe satiṃ labhitvā‘‘ ahaṃ tava bhikkhuṃ pamuṭṭho’’ ti āha. 
591131,122,1623,32,73,1,236,33,"Mahāduggato tikhiṇāya sattiyā kucchiyaṃ pahaṭo viya,‘‘ sāmi, kasmā maṃ nāsesi, ahaṃ tayā hiyyo samādapito bhariyāya saddhiṃ divasaṃ bhatiṃ katvā ajja pātova paṇṇatthāya nadītīre āhiṇḍitvā āgato, dehi me ekaṃ bhikkhun’’ ti bāhā paggayha paridevi. "
