591138,122,1623,148,154,1,36,6,So tesaṃ vacanena maṅkubhūto taṃ āha–
591139,122,1623,155,207,1,350,41,"‘‘ samma mahāduggata, mā maṃ nāsayi, ahaṃ tava kāraṇā mahāvihesaṃ patto, manussā paṇṇe āropitaniyāmena attano attano pattabhikkhū nayiṃsu, attano gehe nisinnabhikkhuṃ nīharitvā dento nāma natthi, satthā pana mukhaṃ dhovitvā gandhakuṭiyameva nisinno, rājayuvarājasenāpatiādayo satthu gandhakuṭito nikkhamanaṃ olokentā nisinnā satthu pattaṃ gahetvā‘ gamissāmā’ ti. "
591140,122,1623,208,240,1,155,23,"Buddhā nāma duggate anukampaṃ karonti, tvaṃ vihāraṃ gantvā‘ duggatomhi, bhante, mama saṅgahaṃ karothā’ ti satthāraṃ vanda, sace te puññaṃ atthi, addhā lacchasī’’ ti. "
591141,122,1624,2,5,1,18,3,So vihāraṃ agamāsi. 
591142,122,1624,6,30,1,137,17,"Atha naṃ aññesu divasesu vihāre vighāsādabhāvena diṭṭhattā rājayuvarājādayo,‘‘ mahāduggata, na tāva bhattakālo, kasmā tvaṃ āgacchasī’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
591143,122,1624,31,44,1,36,7,"So‘‘ jānāmi, sāmi,‘ na tāva bhattakālo’ ti. "
591144,122,1624,45,82,1,204,27,"Satthāraṃ pana vandituṃ āgacchāmī’’ ti vadanto gantvā gandhakuṭiyā ummāre sīsaṃ ṭhapetvā pañcapatiṭṭhitena vanditvā,‘‘ bhante, imasmiṃ nagare mayā duggatataro natthi, avassayo me hotha, karotha me saṅgahan’’ ti āha. "
591145,122,1624,83,91,1,71,8,Satthā gandhakuṭidvāraṃ vivaritvā pattaṃ nīharitvā tassa hatthe ṭhapesi. 
591146,122,1624,92,102,1,84,9,"So cakkavattisiriṃ patto viya ahosi, rājayuvarājādayo aññamaññassa mukhāni olokayiṃsu. "
591147,122,1624,103,112,1,71,8,Satthārā dinnapattañhi koci issariyavasena gahetuṃ samattho nāma natthi. 
591148,122,1624,113,143,1,139,22,"Evaṃ pana vadiṃsu,‘‘ samma mahāduggata, satthu pattaṃ amhākaṃ dehi ettakaṃ nāma te dhanaṃ dassāma, tvaṃ duggato dhanaṃ gaṇhāhi, kiṃ te pattenā’’ ti? "
591149,122,1624,144,162,1,82,12,"Mahāduggato‘‘ na kassaci dassāmi, na me dhanena attho, satthāraṃyeva bhojessāmī’’ ti āha. "
591150,122,1624,163,169,1,47,6,Avasesā taṃ yācitvā pattaṃ alabhitvā nivattiṃsu. 
591151,122,1624,170,216,1,297,38,"Rājā pana‘‘ mahāduggato dhanena palobhiyamānopi satthu pattaṃ na deti, satthārā ca sayaṃ dinnapattaṃ koci gahetuṃ na sakkoti, imassa deyyadhammo nāma kittako bhavissati, iminā deyyadhammassa dinnakāle satthāraṃ ādāya gehaṃ netvā mayhaṃ sampāditaṃ āhāraṃ dassāmī’’ ti cintetvā satthārā saddhiṃyeva agamāsi. "
591152,122,1624,217,226,1,108,9,Sakkopi devarājā yāgukhajjakabhattasūpeyyapaṇṇādīni sampādetvā satthu nisīdanārahaṃ āsanaṃ paññapetvā nisīdi. 
591153,122,1625,2,14,1,51,7,"Mahāduggato satthāraṃ netvā‘‘ pavisatha, bhante’’ ti āha. "
591154,122,1625,15,23,1,56,7,"Vasanagehañcassa nīcaṃ hoti, anonatena pavisituṃ na sakkā. "
591155,122,1625,24,32,1,52,8,Buddhā ca nāma gehaṃ pavisantā na onamitvā pavisanti. 
