591207,122,1628,175,185,1,37,5,"‘‘ amma, therassa santike pabbajissāmī’’ ti."
591208,122,1628,186,259,1,367,48,"‘‘ Sādhu, tāta,‘ ahaṃ tava ajjhāsayaṃ na bhindissāmicceva manaṃ uppādesin’’’ ti vatvā theraṃ nimantetvā bhojetvā,‘‘ bhante, dāso vo pabbajitukāmo, ahaṃ imaṃ sāyanhasamaye vihāraṃ ānessāmī’’ ti theraṃ uyyojetvā ñātake sannipātāpetvā‘‘ mama puttassa gihikāle kattabbasakkāraṃ ajjeva karissāmā’’ ti mahantaṃ sakkāraṃ kāretvā taṃ ādāya vihāraṃ gantvā‘‘ imaṃ, bhante, pabbājethā’’ ti therassa adāsi. "
591209,122,1629,2,31,1,159,19,"Thero pabbajjāya dukkarabhāvaṃ ācikkhitvā‘‘ karissāmahaṃ, bhante, tumhākaṃ ovādan’’ ti vutte‘‘ tena hi ehī’’ ti kese temetvā tacapañcakakammaṭṭhānaṃ ācikkhitvā pabbājesi. "
591210,122,1629,32,46,1,147,14,Mātāpitaropissa sattāhaṃ vihāreyeva vasantā buddhappamukhassa bhikkhusaṅghassa rohitamaccharaseneva dānaṃ datvā sattame divase sāyaṃ gehaṃ agamaṃsu. 
591211,122,1629,47,59,1,92,11,"Thero aṭṭhame divase antogāmaṃ gacchanto taṃ ādāya gacchati, bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ nāgamāsi. "
591212,122,1629,60,62,1,10,2,Kiṃ kāraṇā? 
591213,122,1629,63,77,1,105,13,"Na tāvassa pattacīvaraggahaṇāni vā iriyāpatho vā pāsādiko hoti, apica vihāre therassa kattabbavattaṃ atthi. "
591214,122,1629,78,96,1,211,18,Thero hi bhikkhusaṅghe antogāmaṃ paviṭṭhe sakalavihāraṃ vicaranto asammajjanaṭṭhānaṃ sammajjitvā tucchabhājanesu pānīyaparibhojanīyāni upaṭṭhapetvā dunnikkhittāni mañcapīṭhādīni paṭisāmetvā pacchā gāmaṃ pavisati. 
591215,122,1629,97,124,1,171,19,Apica‘‘ aññatitthiyā tucchavihāraṃ pavisitvā‘ passatha samaṇassa gotamassa sāvakānaṃ nisinnaṭṭhānānī’ ti vattuṃ mā labhiṃsū’’ ti sakalavihāraṃ paṭijaggitvā pacchā gāmaṃ pavisati. 
591216,122,1629,125,134,1,78,9,Tasmā taṃ divasampi sāmaṇerena pattacīvaraṃ gāhāpetvā divātaraṃ piṇḍāya pāvisi. 
591217,122,1630,2,21,1,95,13,"Sāmaṇero upajjhāyena saddhiṃ gacchanto antarāmagge mātikaṃ disvā,‘‘ bhante, idaṃ kiṃ nāmā’’ ti pucchi."
591218,122,1630,22,31,1,23,4,"‘‘ Mātikā nāma, sāmaṇerā’’ ti."
591219,122,1630,32,40,1,20,4,‘‘ Imāya kiṃ karontī’’ ti?
