591223,122,1630,77,89,1,58,7,"‘‘ Evarūpaṃ acittakaṃ attano icchitaṭṭhānaṃ haranti, bhante’’ ti?"
591224,122,1630,90,96,1,10,2,‘‘ Āmāvuso’’ ti. 
591225,122,1630,97,99,1,10,2,So cintesi–
591226,122,1630,100,124,1,161,19,"‘‘ sace evarūpampi acittakaṃ attano icchiticchitaṭṭhānaṃ haritvā kammaṃ karonti, kasmā sacittakāpi cittaṃ attano vase vattetvā samaṇadhammaṃ kātuṃ na sakkhissantī’’ ti. "
591227,122,1630,125,150,1,131,18,"Atheso purato gacchanto usukāre saradaṇḍakaṃ aggimhi tāpetvā akkhikoṭiyā oloketvā ujukaṃ karonte disvā,‘‘ ime, bhante, ke nāmā’’ ti pucchi."
