591242,122,1630,300,322,1,142,17,"‘‘ sace acittakāni kaṭṭhakaliṅgarāni gahetvā cakkādīni karonti, kasmā sacittakā attano cittaṃ vase vattetvā samaṇadhammaṃ kātuṃ na sakkhissantī’’ ti. "
591243,122,1630,323,343,1,94,13,"So imāni kāraṇāni disvā,‘‘ bhante, sace tumhākaṃ pattacīvare tumhe gaṇheyyātha, ahaṃ nivatteyyan’’ ti. "
591244,122,1630,344,372,1,149,19,"Thero‘‘ ayaṃ adhunā pabbajito daharasāmaṇero maṃ anubandhamāno evaṃ vadetī’’ ti cittaṃ anuppādetvāva‘‘ āhara, sāmaṇerā’’ ti vatvā attano pattacīvaraṃ aggahesi. "
591245,122,1631,2,20,1,111,12,"Sāmaṇeropi upajjhāyaṃ vanditvā nivattanto,‘‘ bhante, mayhaṃ āhāraṃ āharanto rohitamaccharaseneva āhareyyāthā’’ ti āha."
