591263,122,1632,208,223,1,104,13,"Tato gantvā dvārakoṭṭhake ṭhatvā sampattaṃ theraṃ cattāro pañhe pucchi, puṭṭhaṃ puṭṭhaṃ pañhaṃ vissajjesi. "
