591307,122,1642,2,4,1,29,2,6 . Lakuṇḍakabhaddiyattheravatthu 
591308,122,1643,2,14,1,98,10,Selo {yathā}ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto lakuṇḍakabhaddiyattheraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
591309,122,1644,2,27,1,135,17,"Puthujjanā kira sāmaṇerādayo theraṃ disvā sīsepi kaṇṇesupi nāsāyapi gahetvā‘‘ kiṃ, cūḷapita, sāsanasmiṃ na ukkaṇṭhasi, abhiramasī’’ ti vadanti. "
591310,122,1644,28,35,1,35,6,"Thero tesu neva kujjhati, na dussati. "
591311,122,1644,36,59,1,151,16,"Dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ passathāvuso, lakuṇḍakabhaddiyattheraṃ disvā sāmaṇerādayo evañcevañca viheṭhenti, so tesu neva kujjhati, na dussatī’’ ti. "
