591415,122,1685,2,13,1,90,10,Na {attahetū}ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto dhammikattheraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
591416,122,1686,2,9,1,61,7,Sāvatthiyaṃ kireko upāsako dhammena samena agāraṃ ajjhāvasati. 
591417,122,1686,10,21,1,86,10,So pabbajitukāmo hutvā ekadivasaṃ bhariyāya saddhiṃ nisīditvā sukhakathaṃ kathento āha–
591418,122,1686,22,31,1,31,4,"‘‘ bhadde, icchāmahaṃ pabbajitun’’ ti."
591419,122,1686,32,50,1,65,10,"‘‘ Tena hi, sāmi, āgamehi tāva , yāvāhaṃ kucchigataṃ dārakaṃ vijāyāmī’’ ti. "
591420,122,1686,51,91,1,212,29,"So āgametvā dārakassa padasā gamanakāle puna taṃ āpucchitvā‘‘ āgamehi tāva, sāmi, yāvāyaṃ vayappatto hotī’’ ti vutte‘‘ kiṃ me imāya apalokitāya vā anapalokitāya vā, attano dukkhanissaraṇaṃ karissāmī’’ ti nikkhamitvā pabbaji. "
591421,122,1686,92,108,1,149,16,So kammaṭṭhānaṃ gahetvā ghaṭento vāyamanto attano pabbajitakiccaṃ niṭṭhapetvā tesaṃ dassanatthāya puna sāvatthiṃ gantvā puttassa dhammakathaṃ kathesi. 
591422,122,1686,109,121,1,73,10,"Sopi nikkhamitvā pabbaji, pabbajitvā ca pana na cirasseva arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. "
591423,122,1686,122,154,1,187,24,"Purāṇadutiyikāpissa‘‘ yesaṃ atthāya ahaṃ gharāvāse vaseyyaṃ, te ubhopi pabbajitā, idāni me kiṃ gharāvāsena, pabbajissāmī’’ ti nikkhamitvā pabbaji, pabbajitvā ca pana na cirasseva arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. "
