591656,122,1781,77,145,1,488,50,"Thero‘‘ nāyaṃ bhikkhu mayā pahaṭo’’ ti avatvāva attano guṇakathaṃ kathento‘‘ yassa nūna, bhante, kāye kāyagatāsati anupaṭṭhitā assa, so idha aññataraṃ sabrahmacāriṃ āsajja appaṭinissajja cārikaṃ pakkameyyā’’ ti vatvā‘‘ seyyathāpi, bhante, pathaviyaṃ sucimpi nikkhipanti, asucimpi nikkhipantī’’ tiādinā nayena attano pathavīsamacittatañca āpotejovāyo rajoharaṇacaṇḍālakumārakausabhachinnavisāṇasamacittatañca ahikuṇapādīhi viya attano kāyena aṭṭiyanañca medakathālikā viya attano kāyapariharaṇañca pakāsesi. "
