591878,122,1825,224,246,1,180,22,So puriso ettakaṃ kammaṃ katvā āyupariyosāne devaloke nibbattitvā ettakaṃ kālaṃ saṃsaranto ekasmiṃ samaye devalokā cavitvā bārāṇasiyaṃ rājakule nibbatto pitu accayena rajjaṃ pāpuṇi. 
591879,122,1825,247,273,1,107,17,"So‘‘ ekaṃ nagaraṃ gaṇhissāmī’’ ti gantvā parivāresi, nāgarānañca sāsanaṃ pahiṇi‘‘ rajjaṃ vā me dentu yuddhaṃ vā’’ ti. "
591880,122,1825,274,294,1,109,14,"Te‘‘ neva rajjaṃ dassāma, na yuddhan’’ ti vatvā cūḷadvārehi nikkhamitvā dārūdakādīni āharanti, sabbakiccāni karonti. "
591881,122,1826,2,11,1,86,9,Itaropi cattāri mahādvārāni rakkhanto sattamāsādhikāni satta vassāni nagaraṃ uparundhi. 
591882,122,1826,12,55,1,170,27,"Athassa mātā‘‘ kiṃ me putto karotī’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ idaṃ nāma devī’’ ti taṃ pavattiṃ sutvā‘‘ bālo mama putto, gacchatha, tassa‘ cūḷadvārānipi pidhāya nagaraṃ uparundhatū’ ti vadethā’’ ti. "
591883,122,1826,56,62,1,33,6,So mātu sāsanaṃ sutvā tathā akāsi. 
591884,122,1826,63,75,1,93,12,Nāgarāpi bahi nikkhamituṃ alabhantā sattame divase attano rājānaṃ māretvā tassa rajjaṃ adaṃsu. 
591885,122,1826,76,113,1,298,35,"So imaṃ kammaṃ katvā āyupariyosāne avīcimhi nibbattitvā yāvāyaṃ pathavī yojanamattaṃ ussannā, tāva niraye paccitvā catunnaṃ cūḷadvārānaṃ pidahitattā tato cuto tassā eva mātu kucchismiṃ paṭisandhiṃ gahetvā sattamāsādhikāni satta vassāni antokucchismiṃ vasitvā satta divasāni yonimukhe tiriyaṃ nipajji. "
591886,122,1826,114,143,1,209,26,"Evaṃ, bhikkhave, sīvali, tadā nagaraṃ uparundhitvā gahitakammena ettakaṃ kālaṃ niraye paccitvā catunnaṃ cūḷadvārānaṃ pidahitattā tato cuto tassā eva mātu kucchiyaṃ paṭisandhiṃ gahetvā ettakaṃ kālaṃ kucchiyaṃ vasi. "
591887,122,1826,144,148,1,49,4,Navamadhuno dinnattā lābhaggayasaggappatto jātoti. 
591888,122,1827,2,7,1,42,4,Punekadivasaṃ bhikkhū kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ–
591889,122,1827,8,26,1,102,12,"‘‘ aho sāmaṇerassa lābho, aho puññaṃ, yena ekakena pañcannaṃ bhikkhusatānaṃ pañcakūṭāgārasatādīni katānī’’ ti. "
591890,122,1827,27,74,1,207,29,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte,‘‘ bhikkhave, mayhaṃ puttassa neva puññaṃ atthi, na pāpaṃ, ubhayamassa pahīnan’’ ti vatvā brāhmaṇavagge imaṃ gāthamāha–"
591891,122,1828,2,11,1,42,6,"‘ ‘ Yodha puññañca pāpañca, ubho saṅgamupaccagā; "
591892,122,1829,2,20,1,49,7,"Asokaṃ virajaṃ suddhaṃ, tamahaṃ brūmi brāhmaṇan’’ ti.( dha. pa.412); "
