591973,122,1851,25,44,1,82,13,"Satthā‘‘ kiṃ, bhikkhave,‘ mayā desitadhammassa appaṃ vā bahuṃ vā’ ti mā pamāṇaṃ gaṇhatha. "
591974,122,1851,45,59,1,93,12,Ekavācāpi hi atthanissitā seyyāvā’’ ti vatvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā dhammaṃ desento imaṃ gāthamāha– 
