592062,122,1872,2,4,1,23,2,3 . Kuṇḍalakesittherīvatthu 
592063,122,1873,2,17,1,98,12,Yo ca gāthāsataṃ {bhāse}ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto kuṇḍalakesiṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
592064,122,1874,2,11,1,82,9,Rājagahe kira ekā seṭṭhidhītā soḷasavassuddesikā abhirūpā ahosi dassanīyā pāsādikā. 
592065,122,1874,12,19,1,58,7,Tasmiñca vaye ṭhitā nāriyo purisajjhāsayā honti purisalolā. 
592066,122,1874,20,28,1,80,8,Atha naṃ mātāpitaro sattabhūmikassa pāsādassa uparimatale sirigabbhe nivāsāpesuṃ. 
592067,122,1874,29,33,1,35,4,Ekamevassā dāsiṃ paricārikaṃ adaṃsu. 
592068,122,1874,34,47,1,119,13,Athekaṃ kulaputtaṃ corakammaṃ karontaṃ gahetvā pacchābāhaṃ bandhitvā catukke catukke kasāhi paharitvā āghātanaṃ nayiṃsu. 
592069,122,1874,48,75,1,168,22,Seṭṭhidhītā mahājanassa saddaṃ sutvā‘‘ kiṃ nu kho etan’’ ti pāsādatale ṭhatvā olokentī taṃ disvā paṭibaddhacittā hutvā taṃ patthayamānā āhāraṃ paṭikkhipitvā mañcake nipajji. 
592070,122,1874,76,80,1,20,4,Atha naṃ mātā pucchi–
592071,122,1874,81,90,1,16,4,"‘‘ kiṃ idaṃ, ammā’’ ti?"
592072,122,1874,91,105,1,65,9,"‘‘ Sace etaṃ‘ coro’ ti gahetvā niyyamānaṃ purisaṃ labhissāmi, jīvissāmi. "
592073,122,1874,106,119,1,54,9,"No ce labhissāmi, jīvitaṃ me natthi, idheva marissāmī’’ ti."
592074,122,1874,120,142,1,93,16,"‘‘ Amma, mā evaṃ kari, amhākaṃ jātiyā ca gottena ca bhogena ca sadisaṃ aññaṃ sāmikaṃ labhissasī’’ ti."
592075,122,1874,143,156,1,56,8,"‘‘ Mayhaṃ aññena kiccaṃ natthi, imaṃ alabhamānā marissāmī’’ ti. "
592076,122,1874,157,163,1,49,6,Mātā dhītaraṃ saññāpetuṃ asakkontī pituno ārocesi. 
592077,122,1874,164,184,1,126,16,Sopi naṃ saññāpetuṃ asakkonto‘‘ kiṃ sakkā kātun’’ ti cintetvā taṃ coraṃ gahetvā gacchantassa rājapurisassa sahassabhaṇḍikaṃ pesesi–
592078,122,1874,185,196,1,40,7,‘‘ imaṃ gahetvā etaṃ purisaṃ mayhaṃ dehī’’ ti. 
592079,122,1874,197,222,1,89,15,"So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti kahāpaṇe gahetvā taṃ muñcitvā aññaṃ māretvā‘‘ mārito, deva, coro’’ ti rañño ārocesi. "
592080,122,1874,223,227,1,29,4,Seṭṭhipi tassa dhītaraṃ adāsi. 
592081,122,1875,2,21,1,129,14,"Sā tato paṭṭhāya‘‘ sāmikaṃ ārādhessāmī’’ ti sabbābharaṇapaṭimaṇḍitā sayameva tassa yāguādīni saṃvidahati, coro katipāhaccayena cintesi–"
592082,122,1875,22,40,1,101,14,‘‘ kadā nu kho imaṃ māretvā etissā ābharaṇāni gahetvā ekasmiṃ surāgehe vikkiṇitvā khādituṃ labhissāmī’’ ti? 
592083,122,1875,41,71,1,121,19,"So‘‘ attheko upāyo’’ ti cintetvā āhāraṃ paṭikkhipitvā mañcake nipajji, atha naṃ sā upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ kiṃ te, sāmi, rujjatī’’ ti pucchi."
592084,122,1875,72,89,1,62,11,"‘‘ Na kiñci me, bhaddeti, kacci pana me mātāpitaro tuyhaṃ kuddhā’’ ti?"
592085,122,1875,90,100,1,22,4,"‘‘ Na kujjhanti, bhadde’’ ti . "
592086,122,1875,101,109,1,19,4,Atha‘‘ kiṃ nāmetan’’ ti?
592087,122,1875,110,149,1,212,28,"‘‘ Bhadde, ahaṃ taṃ divasaṃ bandhitvā niyyamāno corapapāte adhivatthāya devatāya balikammaṃ paṭissuṇitvā jīvitaṃ labhiṃ, tvampi mayā tassā eva ānubhāvena laddhā,‘ taṃ me devatāya balikammaṃ ṭhapitan’ ti cintemi, bhadde’’ ti."
592088,122,1875,150,167,1,55,8,"‘‘ Sāmi, mā cintayi, karissāmi balikammaṃ, vadehi , kenattho’’ ti?"
592089,122,1875,168,177,1,52,5,‘‘ Appodakamadhupāyasena ca lājapañcamakapupphehi cā’’ ti.
592090,122,1875,178,204,1,90,14,"‘‘ Sādhu, sāmi, ahaṃ paṭiyādessāmī’’ ti sā sabbaṃ balikammaṃ paṭiyādetvā‘‘ ehi, sāmi, gacchāmā’’ ti āha."
