592351,122,1953,2,10,1,80,6,"Tattha {abhivādanasīlissā}ti vandanasīlissa, abhiṇhaṃ vandanakiccapasutassāti attho. "
592352,122,1953,11,34,1,190,20,"{Vuḍḍhāpacāyino}ti gihissa vā tadahupabbajite daharasāmaṇerepi, pabbajitassa vā pana pabbajjāya vā upasampadāya vā vuḍḍhatare guṇavuḍḍhe apacāyamānassa, abhivādanena vā niccaṃ pūjentassāti attho. "
592353,122,1953,35,49,1,103,12,"Cattāro dhammā {vaḍḍhantī}ti āyumhi vaḍḍhamāne yattakaṃ kālaṃ taṃ vaḍḍhati, tattakaṃ itarepi vaḍḍhantiyeva. "
592354,122,1953,50,73,1,209,19,"Yena hi paññāsavassaāyusaṃvattanikaṃ kusalaṃ kataṃ, pañcavīsativassakāle cassa jīvitantarāyo uppajjeyya, so abhivādanasīlatāya paṭippassambhati, so yāvatāyukameva tiṭṭhati, vaṇṇādayopissa āyunāva saddhiṃ vaḍḍhanti. "
