592371,122,1959,57,68,1,96,10,"Gabbhamaṃsaṃ jhāyi, aṅgāramatthake pana suvaṇṇabimbasadiso dārako padumagabbhe nipanno viya ahosi. "
592372,122,1959,69,79,1,101,10,Pacchimabhavikassa sattassa hi sinerunā otthariyamānassapi arahattaṃ appatvā jīvitakkhayo nāma natthi. 
