592787,122,2066,106,129,1,113,16,"So satthāraṃ pūjitukāmo hutvā‘‘ sace imaṃ sāṭakaṃ dassāmi, neva brāhmaṇiyā, na mayhaṃ pārupanaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti cintesi. "
