592865,122,2087,177,185,1,13,3,"‘‘ Āma, bhante’’ ti."
592866,122,2087,186,206,1,83,14,"‘‘ Apehi devadhīte, tayā kataṃ vattaṃ kataṃva hotu, ito paṭṭhāya imaṃ ṭhānaṃ mā āgamī’’ ti."
592867,122,2087,207,226,1,78,13,"‘‘ Bhante, mā maṃ nāsetha, tumhākaṃ vattaṃ katvā sampattiṃ me thiraṃ kātuṃ dethā’’ ti."
