592872,122,2088,2,37,1,257,29,"Satthā jetavane gandhakuṭiyaṃ nisinnova tassā roditasaddaṃ sutvā obhāsaṃ pharitvā devadhītāya sammukhe nisīditvā kathento viya‘‘ devadhīte mama puttassa kassapassa saṃvarakaraṇameva bhāro, puññatthikānaṃ pana‘ ayaṃ no attho’ ti sallakkhetvā puññakaraṇameva bhāro. "
