592918,122,2099,197,219,1,149,17,"Satthā kalyāṇapāpakānaṃ kammānaṃ vipākavasena seṭṭhiñceva devatañca ovadanto‘‘ idha, gahapati, pāpapuggalopi yāva pāpaṃ na paccati, tāva bhadrampi passati. "
592919,122,2099,220,228,1,48,7,"Yadā panassa pāpaṃ paccati, tadā pāpameva passati. "
