592929,122,2106,10,18,1,79,8,Sopi hi purimasucaritānubhāvena nibbattaṃ sukhaṃ anubhavamāno bhadrampi passati. 
592930,122,2106,19,34,1,91,14,Yāva pāpaṃ na {paccatī}ti yāvassa taṃ pāpakammaṃ diṭṭhadhamme vā samparāye vā vipākaṃ na deti. 
592931,122,2106,35,58,1,159,21,"Yadā panassa taṃ diṭṭhadhamme vā samparāye vā vipākaṃ deti, atha diṭṭhadhamme vividhā kammakāraṇā, samparāye ca apāyadukkhaṃ anubhonto so pāpo pāpāniyeva passati. "
