592940,122,2111,2,12,1,85,10,So kira yaṃ kiñci mañcapīṭhādibhedaṃ parikkhāraṃ bahi paribhuñjitvā tattheva chaḍḍeti. 
592941,122,2111,13,19,1,54,5,Parikkhāro vassenapi ātapenapi upacikādīhipi vinassati. 
592942,122,2111,20,58,1,149,24,"So bhikkhūhi‘‘ nanu, āvuso, parikkhāro nāma paṭisāmitabbo’’ ti vutte‘‘ appakaṃ mayā kataṃ, āvuso, etaṃ, na etassa cittaṃ atthi, na pittan’’ ti vatvā tatheva karoti. "
