592944,122,2111,65,80,1,70,11,Satthā taṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ bhikkhu evaṃ karosī’’ ti pucchi. 
592945,122,2111,81,106,1,120,19,"So satthārā pucchitopi‘‘ kiṃ etaṃ bhagavā appakaṃ mayā kataṃ, na tassa cittaṃ atthi, nāssa pittan’’ ti tatheva avamaññanto āha. "
592946,122,2111,107,126,1,92,14,"Atha naṃ satthā‘‘ bhikkhūhi evaṃ kātuṃ na vaṭṭati, pāpakammaṃ nāma‘ appakan’ ti na avamaññitabbaṃ. "
592947,122,2111,127,163,1,247,30,"Ajjhokāse ṭhapitañhi vivaṭamukhaṃ bhājanaṃ deve vassante kiñcāpi ekabindunā na pūrati, punappunaṃ vassante pana pūrateva, evamevaṃ pāpaṃ karonto puggalo anupubbena mahantaṃ pāparāsiṃ karotī’’ ti vatvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā dhammaṃ desento imaṃ gāthamāha– "
592948,122,2112,2,4,1,0,0,121.
