592952,122,2116,2,7,1,35,4,Tattha {māvamaññethā}ti na avajāneyya. 
592953,122,2116,8,11,1,15,2,{Pāpassā}ti pāpaṃ. 
592954,122,2116,12,33,1,109,15,"Na mandaṃ {āgamissatī}ti‘‘ appamattakaṃ me pāpakaṃ kataṃ, kadā etaṃ vipaccissatī’’ ti evaṃ pāpaṃ nāvajāneyyāti attho. "
592955,122,2116,34,64,1,232,27,"{Udakumbhopī}ti deve vassante mukhaṃ vivaritvā ṭhapitaṃ yaṃ kiñci kulālabhājanaṃ yathā taṃ ekekassāpi udakabinduno nipātena anupubbena pūrati, evaṃ bālapuggalo thokaṃ thokampi pāpaṃ ācinanto karonto vaḍḍhento pāpassa {pūratiyevā}ti attho. "
