592962,122,2121,11,16,1,47,5,Athekadivasaṃ satthā anumodanaṃ karonto evamāha–
592963,122,2122,2,13,1,57,9,"‘ ‘ Upāsakā idhekacco attanāva dānaṃ deti, paraṃ na samādapeti. "
592964,122,2122,14,21,1,67,6,"So nibbattanibbattaṭṭhāne bhogasampadaṃ labhati, no parivārasampadaṃ. "
592965,122,2122,22,30,1,44,7,"Ekacco attanā dānaṃ na deti, paraṃ samādapeti. "
592966,122,2122,31,39,1,67,6,"So nibbattanibbattaṭṭhāne parivārasampadaṃ labhati, no bhogasampadaṃ. "
592967,122,2122,40,49,1,46,8,"Ekacco attanā ca na deti, parañca na samādapeti. "
592968,122,2122,50,62,1,97,10,"So nibbattanibbattaṭṭhāne neva bhogasampadaṃ labhati, na parivārasampadaṃ, vighāsādo hutvā vicarati. "
