592984,122,2124,149,174,1,164,20,"‘‘ sace me so parisamajjhe avaṇṇaṃ bhāsissati, mama nāme gahitamatteyeva naṃ paharitvā māressāmī’’ ti nivāsanantare churikaṃ bandhitvā punadivase gantvā bhattagge aṭṭhāsi. "
