593132,122,2158,2,15,1,106,12,Yo {appaduṭṭhassā}ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto kokaṃ nāma sunakhaluddakaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
593133,122,2159,2,34,1,206,26,"So kira ekadivasaṃ pubbaṇhasamaye dhanuṃ ādāya sunakhaparivuto araññaṃ gacchanto antarāmagge ekaṃ piṇḍāya pavisantaṃ bhikkhuṃ disvā kujjhitvā‘‘ kāḷakaṇṇi me diṭṭho, ajja kiñci na labhissāmī’’ ti cintetvā pakkāmi. "
593134,122,2159,35,43,1,64,8,Theropi gāme piṇḍāya caritvā katabhattakicco puna vihāraṃ pāyāsi. 
593135,122,2159,44,81,1,225,31,"Itaropi araññe vicaritvā kiñci alabhitvā paccāgacchanto puna theraṃ disvā‘‘ ajjāhaṃ imaṃ kāḷakaṇṇiṃ disvā araññaṃ gato kiñci na labhiṃ, idāni me punapi abhimukho jāto, sunakhehi naṃ khādāpessāmī’’ ti saññaṃ datvā sunakhe vissajjesi. "
