593446,122,2246,163,183,1,96,15,"‘‘ Ime kira tayā saddhiṃ itthiṃ vicarantiṃ disvā vadanti, tvaṃ kasmā kathesi , ete tāva disvā kathenti. "
593447,122,2246,184,209,1,138,21,"Tvaṃ adisvāva imehi saddhiṃ kasmā kathesi, nanu pubbe taveva pāpikaṃ diṭṭhiṃ nissāya idaṃ jātaṃ, idāni kasmā puna pāpikaṃ diṭṭhiṃ gaṇhāsī’’ ti. "
