593449,122,2246,226,282,1,358,47,"Atha nesaṃ satthā tassa pubbakammaṃ kathetvā‘‘ bhikkhu idaṃ pāpakammaṃ nissāya tvaṃ imaṃ vippakāraṃ patto, idāni te puna tathārūpaṃ pāpikaṃ diṭṭhiṃ gahetuṃ na yuttaṃ, mā puna bhikkhūhi saddhiṃ kiñci kathehi, nissaddo mukhavaṭṭiyaṃ chinnakaṃsathālasadiso hohi, evaṃ karonto nibbānappatto nāma bhavissatī’’ ti vatvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā dhammaṃ desento imā gāthā abhāsi– "
