594187,122,2449,2,12,1,92,10,Appassutāyan ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto lāḷudāyittheraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
594188,122,2450,2,97,1,278,36,"So kira maṅgalaṃ karontānaṃ gehaṃ gantvā‘‘ tirokuṭṭesu tiṭṭhantī’’ tiādinā( khu. pā.7.1; pe. va.14) nayena avamaṅgalaṃ katheti, avamaṅgalaṃ karontānaṃ gehaṃ gantvā tirokuṭṭādīsu kathetabbesu‘‘ dānañca dhammacariyā cā’’ tiādinā( khu. pā.5.7; su. ni.266) nayena maṅgalagāthā vā‘‘ yaṃ kiñci vittaṃ idha vā huraṃ vā’’ ti ratanasuttaṃ( khu. pā.6.3; su. ni.226) vā katheti. "
594189,122,2450,98,120,1,86,14,Evaṃ tesu tesu ṭhānesu‘‘ aññaṃ kathessāmī’’ ti aññaṃ kathentopi‘‘ aññaṃ kathemī’’ ti na jānāti. 
594190,122,2450,121,127,1,42,6,Bhikkhū tassa kathaṃ sutvā satthu ārocesuṃ–
594191,122,2450,128,146,1,94,10,"‘‘ kiṃ, bhante, lāḷudāyissa maṅgalāmaṅgalaṭṭhānesu gamanena, aññasmiṃ kathetabbe aññameva kathetī’’ ti. "
594192,122,2450,147,169,1,109,15,"Satthā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idānevesa evaṃ katheti, pubbepi aññasmiṃ kathetabbe aññameva kathesī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari– "
594193,122,2451,2,13,1,97,11,Atīte kira bārāṇasiyaṃ aggidattassa nāma brāhmaṇassa putto somadattakumāro nāma rājānaṃ upaṭṭhahi. 
594194,122,2451,14,19,1,26,5,So raññā piyo ahosi manāpo. 
594195,122,2451,20,25,1,39,5,Brāhmaṇo pana kasikammaṃ nissāya jīvati. 
594196,122,2451,26,30,1,25,4,Tassa dveyeva goṇā ahesuṃ. 
594197,122,2451,31,34,1,13,3,Tesu eko mato. 
594198,122,2451,35,38,1,19,3,Brāhmaṇo puttaṃ āha–
594199,122,2451,39,54,1,53,9,"‘‘ tāta, somadatta, rājānaṃ me yācitvā ekaṃ goṇaṃ āharā’’ ti. "
594200,122,2451,55,96,1,160,24,"Somadatto‘‘ sacāhaṃ rājānaṃ yācissāmi, lahubhāvo me paññāyissatī’’ ti cintetvā‘‘ tumheyeva, tāta, rājānaṃ yācathā’’ ti vatvā‘‘ tena hi, tāta, maṃ gahetvā yāhī’’ ti vutto cintesi–"
594201,122,2451,97,118,1,127,15,"‘‘ ayaṃ brāhmaṇo dandhapañño abhikkamādivacanamattampi na jānāti, aññasmiṃ vattabbe aññameva vadati, sikkhāpetvā pana naṃ nessāmī’’ ti. "
594202,122,2451,119,191,1,386,53,"So taṃ ādāya bīraṇatthambhakaṃ nāma susānaṃ gantvā tiṇakalāpe bandhitvā‘‘ ayaṃ rājā, ayaṃ uparājā, ayaṃ senāpatī’’ ti nāmāni katvā paṭipāṭiyā pitu dassetvā‘‘ tumhehi rājakulaṃ gantvā evaṃ abhikkamitabbaṃ, evaṃ paṭikkamitabbaṃ, evaṃ nāma rājā vattabbo, evaṃ nāma uparājā, rājānaṃ pana upasaṅkamitvā‘ jayatu bhavaṃ, mahārājā’ ti vatvā evaṃ ṭhatvā imaṃ gāthaṃ vatvā goṇaṃ yāceyyāthā’’ ti gāthaṃ uggaṇhāpesi–"
594203,122,2452,2,12,1,42,8,"‘ ‘ Dve me goṇā mahārāja, yehi khettaṃ kasāmase; "
594204,122,2453,2,13,1,43,8,"Tesu eko mato deva, dutiyaṃ dehi khattiyā’’ ti. "
594205,122,2454,2,75,1,416,52,"So hi saṃvaccharamattena taṃ gāthaṃ paguṇaṃ katvā paguṇabhāvaṃ puttassa ārocetvā‘‘ tena hi, tāta, kañcideva paṇṇākāraṃ ādāya āgacchatha, ahaṃ purimataraṃ gantvā rañño santike ṭhassāmī’’ ti vutte‘‘ sādhu, tātā’’ ti paṇṇākāraṃ gahetvā somadattassa rañño santike ṭhitakāle ussāhappatto rājakulaṃ gantvā raññā tuṭṭhacittena katapaṭisammodano,‘‘ tāta, cirassaṃ vata āgatattha, idamāsanaṃ nisīditvā vadatha, yenattho’’ ti vutte imaṃ gāthamāha–"
594206,122,2455,2,12,1,42,8,"‘ ‘ Dve me goṇā mahārāja, yehi khettaṃ kasāmase; "
594207,122,2456,2,13,1,44,8,"Tesu eko mato deva, dutiyaṃ gaṇha khattiyā’’ ti. "
594208,122,2457,2,19,1,62,11,"Raññā ‘‘ kiṃ vadesi, tāta, puna vadehī’’ ti vuttepi tameva gāthaṃ āha. "
594209,122,2457,20,66,1,286,35,"Rājā tena virajjhitvā kathitabhāvaṃ ñatvā sitaṃ katvā,‘‘ somadatta, tumhākaṃ gehe bahū maññe goṇā’’ ti vatvā‘‘ tumhehi dinnā bahū bhavissanti, devā’’ ti vutte bodhisattassa tussitvā brāhmaṇassa soḷasa goṇe alaṅkārabhaṇḍakaṃ nivāsagāmañcassa brahmadeyyaṃ datvā mahantena yasena brāhmaṇaṃ uyyojesīti. "
594210,122,2458,2,40,1,208,26,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā‘‘ tadā rājā ānando ahosi, brāhmaṇo lāḷudāyī, somadatto pana ahamevā’’ ti jātakaṃ samodhānetvā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva, pubbepesa attano appassutatāya aññasmiṃ vattabbe aññameva vadati. "
594211,122,2458,41,52,1,68,9,Appassutapuriso hi balibaddasadiso nāma hotī’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– 
594212,122,2459,2,4,1,0,0,152.
594213,122,2460,2,9,1,38,5,"‘ ‘ Appassutāyaṃ puriso, balibaddova jīrati; "
594214,122,2461,2,13,1,50,8,"Maṃsāni tassa vaḍḍhanti, paññā tassa na vaḍḍhatī’’ ti. "
594215,122,2462,2,11,1,56,8,Tattha appassutāyan ti ekassa vā dvinnaṃ vā paṇṇāsakānaṃ. 
594216,122,2462,12,27,1,109,15,Atha vā pana vaggānaṃ sabbantimena paricchedena ekassa vā dvinnaṃ vā suttantānaṃ vāpi abhāvena appassuto ayaṃ. 
594217,122,2462,28,33,1,51,5,Kammaṭṭhānaṃ pana uggahetvā anuyuñjanto bahussutova. 
594218,122,2462,34,122,1,613,69,"Balibaddova {jīratī}ti yathā hi balibaddo jīramāno vaḍḍhamāno neva mātu, na pitu, na sesañātakānaṃ atthāya vaḍḍhati, atha kho niratthakameva jīrati, evamevaṃ ayampi na upajjhāyavattaṃ karoti, na ācariyavattaṃ, na āgantukavattādīni, na bhāvanārāmataṃ anuyuñjati, niratthakameva jīrati, maṃsāni tassa {vaḍḍhantī}ti yathā balibaddassa‘‘ yuganaṅgalādīni vahituṃ asamattho eso’’ ti araññe vissaṭṭhassa tattheva vicarantassa khādantassa pivantassa maṃsāni vaḍḍhanti, evameva imassāpi upajjhāyādīhi vissaṭṭhassa saṅghaṃ nissāya cattāro paccaye labhitvā uddhavirecanādīni katvā kāyaṃ posentassa maṃsāni vaḍḍhanti, thūlasarīro hutvā vicarati. "
594219,122,2462,123,146,1,168,21,"Paññā {tassā}ti lokiyalokuttarā panassa paññā ekaṅgulamattāpi na vaḍḍhati, araññe pana gacchalatādīni viya cha dvārāni nissāya taṇhā ceva navavidhamāno ca vaḍḍhatīti attho. "
594220,122,2463,2,6,1,49,4,Desanāvasāne mahājano sotāpattiphalādīni pāpuṇīti. 
594221,122,2464,2,4,1,29,2,Lāḷudāyittheravatthu sattamaṃ.
594222,122,2465,2,4,1,11,2,8 . Udānavatthu 
594223,122,2466,2,15,1,132,13,Anekajātisaṃsāran ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā bodhirukkhamūle nisinno udānavasena udānetvā aparabhāge ānandattherena puṭṭho kathesi. 
594224,122,2467,2,38,1,393,36,So hi bodhirukkhamūle nisinno sūriye anatthaṅgateyeva mārabalaṃ viddhaṃsetvā paṭhamayāme pubbenivāsapaṭicchādakaṃ tamaṃ padāletvā majjhimayāme dibbacakkhuṃ visodhetvā pacchimayāme sattesu kāruññataṃ paṭicca paccayākāre ñāṇaṃ otāretvā taṃ anulomapaṭilomavasena sammasanto aruṇuggamanavelāya sammāsambodhiṃ abhisambujjhitvā anekehi buddhasatasahassehi avijahitaṃ udānaṃ udānento imā gāthā abhāsi– 
594225,122,2468,2,4,1,0,0,153.
594226,122,2469,2,8,1,40,4,"‘ ‘ Anekajātisaṃsāraṃ, sandhāvissaṃ anibbisaṃ; "
594227,122,2470,2,8,1,42,5,"Gahakāraṃ gavesanto, dukkhā jāti punappunaṃ. "
594228,122,2471,2,4,1,0,0,154.
594229,122,2472,2,13,1,40,7,"‘ ‘ Gahakāraka diṭṭhosi, puna gehaṃ na kāhasi; "
594230,122,2473,2,9,1,45,6,"Sabbā te phāsukā bhaggā, gahakūṭaṃ visaṅkhataṃ; "
594231,122,2474,2,10,1,48,5,"Visaṅkhāragataṃ cittaṃ, taṇhānaṃ khayamajjhagā’’ ti. "
594232,122,2475,2,41,1,366,35,"Tattha gahakāraṃ {gavesanto}ti ahaṃ imassa attabhāvasaṅkhātassa gehassa kārakaṃ taṇhāvaḍḍhakiṃ gavesanto yena ñāṇena sakkā taṃ daṭṭhuṃ , tassa bodhiñāṇassatthāya dīpaṅkarapādamūle katābhinīhāro ettakaṃ kālaṃ anekajātisaṃsāraṃ anekajātisatasahassasaṅkhātaṃ imaṃ saṃsāravaṭṭaṃ anibbisaṃ taṃ ñāṇaṃ avindanto alabhantoyeva sandhāvissaṃ saṃsariṃ, aparāparaṃ anuvicarinti attho. "
594233,122,2475,42,49,1,66,7,Dukkhā jāti punappunan ti idaṃ gahakārakagavesanassa kāraṇavacanaṃ. 
594234,122,2475,50,64,1,105,13,"Yasmā jarābyādhimaraṇamissitāya jāti nāmesā punappunaṃ upagantuṃ dukkhā, na ca sā tasmiṃ adiṭṭhe nivattati. "
594235,122,2475,65,70,1,40,5,Tasmā taṃ gavesanto sandhāvissanti attho. 
594236,122,2475,71,78,1,63,6,{Diṭṭhosī}ti sabbaññutaññāṇaṃ paṭivijjhantena mayā idāni diṭṭhosi. 
594237,122,2475,79,90,1,79,11,Puna gehan ti puna imasmiṃ saṃsāravaṭṭe attabhāvasaṅkhātaṃ mama gehaṃ na kāhasi. 
594238,122,2475,91,102,1,70,10,Sabbā te phāsukā {bhaggā}ti tava sabbā avasesā kilesaphāsukā mayā bhaggā. 
594239,122,2475,103,115,1,113,11,Gahakūṭaṃ visaṅkhatan ti imassa tayā katassa attabhāvagehassa avijjāsaṅkhātaṃ kaṇṇikamaṇḍalampi mayā viddhaṃsitaṃ. 
594240,122,2475,116,127,1,104,11,Visaṅkhāragataṃ cittan ti idāni mama cittaṃ visaṅkhāraṃ nibbānaṃ ārammaṇakaraṇavasena gataṃ anupaviṭṭhaṃ. 
594241,122,2475,128,135,1,72,6,Taṇhānaṃ {khayamajjhagā}ti taṇhānaṃ khayasaṅkhātaṃ arahattaṃ adhigatosmīti. 
594242,122,2476,2,4,1,20,2,Udānavatthu aṭṭhamaṃ.
594243,122,2477,2,4,1,26,2,9 . Mahādhanaseṭṭhiputtavatthu 
594244,122,2478,2,13,1,103,10,{Acaritvā}ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā isipatane migadāye viharanto mahādhanaseṭṭhiputtaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
594245,122,2479,2,8,1,50,6,So kira bārāṇasiyaṃ asītikoṭivibhave kule nibbatti. 
594246,122,2479,9,12,1,27,3,Athassa mātāpitaro cintesuṃ–
594247,122,2479,13,34,1,123,15,"‘‘ amhākaṃ kule mahābhogakkhandho, puttassa no hatthe ṭhapetvā yathāsukhaṃ paribhogaṃ karissāma, aññena kammena kiccaṃ natthī’’ ti. "
594248,122,2479,35,38,1,40,3,Taṃ naccagītavāditamattameva sikkhāpesuṃ. 
594249,122,2479,39,47,1,69,8,Tasmiṃyeva nagare aññasmiṃ asītikoṭivibhave kule ekā dhītāpi nibbatti. 
594250,122,2479,48,55,1,76,7,Tassāpi mātāpitaro tatheva cintetvā taṃ naccagītavāditamattameva sikkhāpesuṃ. 
594251,122,2479,56,60,1,37,4,Tesaṃ vayappattānaṃ āvāhavivāho ahosi. 
594252,122,2479,61,66,1,44,5,Atha nesaṃ aparabhāge mātāpitaro kālamakaṃsu. 
594253,122,2479,67,72,1,41,4,Dveasītikoṭidhanaṃ ekasmiṃyeva gehe ahosi. 
594254,122,2479,73,80,1,58,6,Seṭṭhiputto divasassa tikkhattuṃ rañño upaṭṭhānaṃ gacchati. 
594255,122,2479,81,86,1,34,5,Atha tasmiṃ nagare dhuttā cintesuṃ–
594256,122,2479,87,104,1,103,11,"‘‘ sacāyaṃ seṭṭhiputto surāsoṇḍo bhavissati, amhākaṃ phāsukaṃ bhavissati, uggaṇhāpema naṃ surāsoṇḍabhāvan’’ ti. "
594257,122,2479,105,150,1,325,38,"Te suraṃ ādāya khajjakamaṃse ceva loṇasakkharā ca dussante bandhitvā mūlakande gahetvā tassa rājakulato āgacchantassa maggaṃ olokayamānā nisīditvā taṃ āgacchantaṃ disvā suraṃ pivitvā loṇasakkharaṃ mukhe khipitvā mūlakandaṃ ḍaṃsitvā‘‘ vassasataṃ jīva sāmi, seṭṭhiputta, taṃ nissāya mayaṃ khādanapivanasamatthā bhaveyyāmā’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
594258,122,2479,151,159,1,64,8,So tesaṃ vacanaṃ sutvā pacchato āgacchantaṃ cūḷūpaṭṭhākaṃ pucchi–
594259,122,2479,160,168,1,18,4,‘‘ kiṃ ete pivantī’’ ti. 
594260,122,2479,169,173,1,19,3,"Ekaṃ pānakaṃ, sāmīti. "
594261,122,2479,174,176,1,20,2,Manāpajātikaṃ etanti. 
594262,122,2479,177,186,1,65,8,"Sāmi, imasmiṃ jīvaloke iminā sadisaṃ pātabbayuttakaṃ nāma natthīti. "
594263,122,2479,187,202,1,69,11,So‘‘ evaṃ sante mayāpi pātuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti thokaṃ thokaṃ āharāpetvā pivati. 
594264,122,2479,203,211,1,66,8,Athassa nacirasseva te dhuttā pivanabhāvaṃ ñatvā taṃ parivārayiṃsu. 
594265,122,2479,212,217,1,34,5,Gacchante kāle parivāro mahā ahosi. 
594266,122,2479,218,253,1,211,28,"So satenapi satadvayenapi suraṃ āharāpetvā pivanto iminā anukkameneva nisinnaṭṭhānādīsu kahāpaṇarāsiṃ ṭhapetvā suraṃ pivanto‘‘ iminā mālā āharatha, iminā gandhe, ayaṃ jano jute cheko, ayaṃ nacce, ayaṃ gīte, ayaṃ vādite. "
594267,122,2479,254,288,1,179,25,"Imassa sahassaṃ detha, imassa dve sahassānī’’ ti evaṃ vikiranto nacirasseva attano santakaṃ asītikoṭidhanaṃ khepetvā‘‘ khīṇaṃ te, sāmi, dhanan’’ ti vutte kiṃ bhariyāya me santakaṃ natthīti. "
594268,122,2479,289,293,1,12,2,"Atthi, sāmīti . "
594269,122,2479,294,298,1,22,4,Tena hi taṃ āharathāti. 
594270,122,2479,299,312,1,159,13,Tampi tatheva khepetvā anupubbena khettaārāmuyyānayoggādikampi antamaso bhājanabhaṇḍakampi attharaṇapāvuraṇanisīdanampi sabbaṃ attano santakaṃ vikkiṇitvā khādi. 
594271,122,2479,313,326,1,90,12,"Atha naṃ mahallakakāle yehissa kulasantakaṃ gehaṃ vikkiṇitvā gahitaṃ, te taṃ gehā nīhariṃsu. "
594272,122,2479,327,342,1,133,15,So bhariyaṃ ādāya parajanassa gehabhittiṃ nissāya vasanto kapālakhaṇḍaṃ ādāya bhikkhāya caritvā janassa ucchiṭṭhakaṃ bhuñjituṃ ārabhi. 
594273,122,2480,2,16,1,136,14,Atha naṃ ekadivasaṃ āsanasālāya dvāre ṭhatvā daharasāmaṇerehi diyyamānaṃ ucchiṭṭhakabhojanaṃ paṭiggaṇhantaṃ disvā satthā sitaṃ pātvākāsi. 
594274,122,2480,17,22,1,40,5,Atha naṃ ānandatthero sitakāraṇaṃ pucchi. 
594275,122,2480,23,41,1,142,14,"Satthā sitakāraṇaṃ kathento‘‘ passānanda, imaṃ mahādhanaseṭṭhiputtaṃ imasmiṃ nagare dveasītikoṭidhanaṃ khepetvā bhariyaṃ ādāya bhikkhāya carantaṃ. "
594276,122,2480,42,55,1,101,12,"Sace hi ayaṃ paṭhamavaye bhoge akhepetvā kammante payojayissa, imasmiṃyeva nagare aggaseṭṭhi abhavissa. "
594277,122,2480,56,67,1,92,9,"Sace pana nikkhamitvā pabbajissa, arahattaṃ pāpuṇissa, bhariyāpissa anāgāmiphale patiṭṭhahissa. "
594278,122,2480,68,82,1,118,12,"Sace majjhimavaye bhoge akhepetvā kammante payojayissa, dutiyaseṭṭhi abhavissa, nikkhamitvā pabbajanto anāgāmī abhavissa. "
594279,122,2480,83,86,1,42,3,Bhariyāpissa sakadāgāmiphale patiṭṭhahissa. 
594280,122,2480,87,107,1,165,15,"Sace pacchimavaye bhoge akhepetvā kammante payojayissa, tatiyaseṭṭhi abhavissa, nikkhamitvā pabbajantopi sakadāgāmī abhavissa , bhariyāpissa sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahissa. "
594281,122,2480,108,113,1,47,5,Idāni panesa gihibhogatopi parihīno sāmaññatopi. 
594282,122,2480,114,128,1,81,12,Parihāyitvā ca pana sukkhapallale koñcasakuṇo viya jāto’’ ti vatvā imā gāthā abhāsi– 
594283,122,2481,2,4,1,0,0,155.
594284,122,2482,2,10,1,45,6,"‘ ‘ Acaritvā brahmacariyaṃ, aladdhā yobbane dhanaṃ; "
594285,122,2483,2,7,1,43,4,"Jiṇṇakoñcāva jhāyanti, khīṇamaccheva pallale. "
594286,122,2484,2,4,1,0,0,156.
594287,122,2485,2,10,1,45,6,"‘ ‘ Acaritvā brahmacariyaṃ, aladdhā yobbane dhanaṃ; "
594288,122,2486,2,10,1,42,5,"Senti cāpātikhīṇāva, purāṇāni anutthunan’’ ti. "
594289,122,2487,2,7,1,44,4,Tattha {acaritvā}ti brahmacariyavāsaṃ avasitvā. 
594290,122,2487,8,21,1,97,12,{Yobbane}ti anuppanne vā bhoge uppādetuṃ uppanne vā bhoge rakkhituṃ samatthakāle dhanampi alabhitvā. 
594291,122,2487,22,35,1,109,12,{Khīṇamacche}ti te evarūpā bālā udakassa abhāvā khīṇamacche pallale parikkhīṇapattā jiṇṇakoñcā viya avajhāyanti. 
594292,122,2487,36,67,1,242,28,"Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti– pallale udakassa abhāvo viya hi imesaṃ vasanaṭṭhānassa abhāvo, macchānaṃ khīṇabhāvo viya imesaṃ bhogānaṃ abhāvo, khīṇapattānaṃ koñcānaṃ uppatitvā gamanābhāvo viya imesaṃ idāni jalathalapathādīhi bhoge saṇṭhāpetuṃ asamatthabhāvo. "
594293,122,2487,68,76,1,62,8,Tasmā te khīṇapattā koñcā viya ettheva bajjhitvā avajhāyantīti. 
594294,122,2487,77,85,1,54,6,"{Cāpātikhīṇāvā}ti cāpato atikhīṇā, cāpā vinimuttāti attho. "
594295,122,2487,86,120,1,222,29,"Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti– yathā cāpā vinimuttā sarā yathāvegaṃ gantvā patitā, taṃ gahetvā ukkhipante asati tattheva upacikānaṃ bhattaṃ honti, evaṃ imepi tayo vaye atikkantā idāni attānaṃ uddharituṃ asamatthatāya maraṇaṃ upagamissanti. "
594296,122,2487,121,123,1,11,2,Tena vuttaṃ–
594297,122,2487,124,131,1,22,3,‘‘ senti cāpātikhīṇāvā’’ ti. 
