594304,122,2493,2,4,1,21,2,1 . Bodhirājakumāravatthu 
594305,122,2494,2,15,1,94,9,{Attānañce}ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā bhesakaḷāvane viharanto bodhirājakumāraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
594306,122,2495,2,17,1,119,15,So kira pathavītale aññehi pāsādehi asadisarūpaṃ ākāse uppatamānaṃ viya kokanudaṃ nāma pāsādaṃ kāretvā vaḍḍhakiṃ pucchi–
594307,122,2495,18,34,1,78,11,"‘‘ kiṃ tayā aññatthāpi evarūpo pāsādo katapubbo, udāhu paṭhamasippameva te idan’’ ti."
594308,122,2495,35,46,1,41,6,"‘‘ Paṭhamasippameva, devā’’ ti ca vutte cintesi–"
594309,122,2495,47,60,1,81,10,"‘‘ sace ayaṃ aññassapi evarūpaṃ pāsādaṃ karissati, ayaṃ pāsādo anacchariyo bhavissati. "
594310,122,2495,61,81,1,113,17,"Imaṃ mayā māretuṃ vā hatthapāde vāssa chindituṃ akkhīni vā uppāṭetuṃ vaṭṭati, evaṃ aññassa pāsādaṃ na karissatī’’ ti. "
594311,122,2495,82,90,1,78,8,So tamatthaṃ attano piyasahāyakassa sañjīvakaputtassa nāma māṇavakassa kathesi. 
594312,122,2495,91,93,1,10,2,So cintesi–
594313,122,2495,94,115,1,99,14,"‘‘ nissaṃsayaṃ esa vaḍḍhakiṃ nāsessati, anaggho sippī, so mayi passante mā nassatu, saññamassa dassāmī’’ ti. "
594314,122,2495,116,150,1,135,20,"So taṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ pāsāde te kammaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ, no’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ niṭṭhitan’’ ti vutte‘‘ rājakumāro taṃ nāsetukāmo attānaṃ rakkheyyāsī’’ ti āha . "
594315,122,2495,151,200,1,200,29,"Vaḍḍhakīpi‘‘ bhaddakaṃ te, sāmi, kataṃ mama ārocentena, ahamettha kattabbaṃ jānissāmī’’ ti vatvā‘‘ kiṃ, samma, amhākaṃ pāsāde kammaṃ niṭṭhitan’’ ti rājakumārena puṭṭho‘‘ na tāva, deva, niṭṭhitaṃ, bahu avasiṭṭhan’’ ti āha. "
594316,122,2495,201,205,1,28,4,Kiṃ kammaṃ nāma avasiṭṭhanti? 
594317,122,2495,206,215,1,49,6,"Pacchā, deva, ācikkhissāmi, dārūni tāva āharāpethāti. "
594318,122,2495,216,219,1,17,3,Kiṃ dārūni nāmāti? 
594319,122,2495,220,224,1,29,3,"Nissārāni sukkhadārūni, devāti. "
594320,122,2495,225,228,1,19,3,So āharāpetvā adāsi. 
594321,122,2495,229,232,1,12,3,Atha naṃ āha–
594322,122,2495,233,243,1,46,7,"‘‘ deva, te ito paṭṭhāya mama santikaṃ nāgantabbaṃ. "
594323,122,2495,244,246,1,10,2,Kiṃ kāraṇā? 
594324,122,2495,247,266,1,130,16,"Sukhumakammaṃ karontassa hi aññehi saddhiṃ sallapantassa me kammavikkhepo hoti, āhāravelāyaṃ pana me bhariyāva āhāraṃ āharissatī’’ ti. "
594325,122,2495,267,275,1,31,4,Rājakumāropi‘‘ sādhū’’ ti paṭissuṇi. 
594326,122,2495,276,293,1,141,17,Sopi ekasmiṃ gabbhe nisīditvā tāni dārūni tacchetvā attano puttadārassa anto nisīdanayoggaṃ garuḷasakuṇaṃ katvā āhāravelāya pana bhariyaṃ āha–
594327,122,2495,294,306,1,62,7,‘‘ gehe vijjamānakaṃ sabbaṃ vikkiṇitvā hiraññasuvaṇṇaṃ gaṇhāhī’’ ti. 
594328,122,2495,307,314,1,79,7,Rājakumāropi vaḍḍhakissa anikkhamanatthāya gehaṃ parikkhipitvā ārakkhaṃ ṭhapesi. 
594329,122,2495,315,339,1,180,19,Vaḍḍhakīpi sakuṇassa niṭṭhitakāle‘‘ ajja sabbepi dārake gahetvā āgaccheyyāsī’’ ti bhariyaṃ vatvā bhuttapātarāso puttadāraṃ sakuṇassa kucchiyaṃ nisīdāpetvā vātapānena nikkhamitvā palāyi. 
594330,122,2495,340,362,1,124,16,"So tesaṃ,‘‘ deva, vaḍḍhakī palāyatī’’ ti kandantānaṃyeva gantvā himavante otaritvā ekaṃ nagaraṃ māpetvā kaṭṭhavāhanarājā nāma jāto. "
594331,122,2496,2,21,1,151,14,Rājakumāropi ‘‘ pāsādamahaṃ karissāmī’’ ti satthāraṃ nimantetvā pāsāde catujjātiyagandhehi paribhaṇḍikaṃ katvā paṭhamaummārato paṭṭhāya celapaṭikaṃ patthari. 
594332,122,2496,22,44,1,106,16,"So kira aputtako, tasmā‘‘ sacāhaṃ puttaṃ vā dhītaraṃ vā lacchāmi, satthā imaṃ akkamissatī’’ ti cintetvā patthari. "
594333,122,2496,45,62,1,93,12,"So satthari āgate satthāraṃ pañcapatiṭṭhitena vanditvā pattaṃ gahetvā‘‘ pavisatha, bhante’’ ti āha. "
594334,122,2496,63,71,1,44,7,"Satthā na pāvisi, so dutiyampi tatiyampi yāci. "
594335,122,2496,72,76,1,41,4,Satthā apavisitvāva ānandattheraṃ olokesi. 
594336,122,2496,77,104,1,180,19,"Thero olokitasaññāyeva vatthānaṃ anakkamanabhāvaṃ ñatvā taṃ‘‘ saṃharatu, rājakumāra, dussāni, na bhagavā celapaṭikaṃ akkamissati, pacchimajanataṃ tathāgato oloketī’’ ti dussāni saṃharāpesi. "
594337,122,2496,105,117,1,112,12,So dussāni saṃharitvā satthāraṃ antonivesanaṃ pavesatvā yāgukhajjakena sammānetvā ekamantaṃ nisinno vanditvā āha–
594338,122,2496,118,142,1,153,18,"‘‘ bhante, ahaṃ tumhākaṃ upakārako tikkhattuṃ saraṇaṃ gato, kucchigato ca kiramhi ekavāraṃ saraṇaṃ gato, dutiyaṃ taruṇadārakakāle, tatiyaṃ viññubhāvaṃ pattakāle. "
594339,122,2496,143,152,1,43,7,Tassa me kasmā celapaṭikaṃ na akkamitthā’’ ti?
594340,122,2496,153,167,1,47,8,"‘‘ Kiṃ pana tvaṃ, kumāra, cintetvā celāni attharī’’ ti?"
594341,122,2496,168,188,1,95,14,"‘‘ Sace puttaṃ vā dhītaraṃ vā lacchāmi, satthā me celapaṭikaṃ akkamissatī’’ ti idaṃ cintetvā, bhanteti. "
594342,122,2496,189,193,1,26,4,Tenevāhaṃ taṃ na akkaminti.
