594347,122,2496,240,249,1,21,4,"‘‘ Kasmiṃ kāle, bhante’’ ti? "
594348,122,2496,250,255,1,38,5,Athassa satthā atītaṃ āharitvā dassesi– 
594349,122,2497,2,10,1,66,8,Atīte kira anekasatā manussā mahatiyā nāvāya samuddaṃ pakkhandiṃsu. 
594350,122,2497,11,14,1,25,3,Nāvā samuddamajjhe bhijji. 
594351,122,2497,15,27,1,89,11,"Dve jayampatikā ekaṃ phalakaṃ gahetvā antaradīpakaṃ pavisiṃsu, sesā sabbe tattheva mariṃsu. "
594352,122,2497,28,35,1,46,6,Tasmiṃ kho pana dīpake mahāsakuṇasaṅgho vasati. 
594353,122,2497,36,51,1,128,14,"Te aññaṃ khāditabbakaṃ adisvā chātajjhattā sakuṇaaṇḍāni aṅgāresu pacitvā khādiṃsu, tesu appahontesu sakuṇacchāpe gahetvā khādiṃsu. "
594354,122,2497,52,57,1,61,5,Evaṃ paṭhamavayepi majjhimavayepi pacchimavayepi khādiṃsuyeva. 
594355,122,2497,58,68,1,68,9,"Ekasmimpi vaye appamādaṃ nāpajjiṃsu, ekopi ca nesaṃ appamādaṃ nāpajji. "
