594371,122,2502,147,166,1,153,16,"Sace pana pabbajito paṭhamavaye sajjhāyaṃ karonto dhārento vācento vattapaṭivattaṃ karonto pamādaṃ āpajjati, majjhimavaye appamattena samaṇadhammo kātabbo. "
594372,122,2502,167,182,1,166,14,"Sace paṭhamavaye uggahitapariyattiyā aṭṭhakathaṃ vinicchayaṃ kāraṇākāraṇañca pucchanto majjhimavaye pamādaṃ āpajjati, pacchimavaye appamattena samaṇadhammo kātabboyeva. "
