594417,122,2517,2,10,1,57,6,Tattha patirūpe {nivesaye}ti anucchavike guṇe patiṭṭhāpeyya. 
594418,122,2517,11,29,1,136,16,"Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti– yo appicchatādiguṇehi vā ariyavaṃsapaṭipadādīhi vā paraṃ anusāsitukāmo, so attānameva paṭhamaṃ tasmiṃ guṇe patiṭṭhāpeyya. "
