594424,122,2520,2,4,1,26,2,3 . Padhānikatissattheravatthu 
594425,122,2521,2,13,1,94,9,{Attānañce}ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto padhānikatissattheraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
594426,122,2522,2,37,1,231,28,"So kira satthu santike kammaṭṭhānaṃ gahetvā pañcasate bhikkhū ādāya araññe vassaṃ upagantvā,‘‘ āvuso, dharamānakassa buddhassa santike vo kammaṭṭhānaṃ gahitaṃ, appamattāva samaṇadhammaṃ karothā’’ ti ovaditvā sayaṃ gantvā nipajjitvā supati. "
594427,122,2522,38,45,1,64,7,Te bhikkhū paṭhamayāme caṅkamitvā majjhimayāme vihāraṃ pavisanti. 
594428,122,2522,46,76,1,169,22,"So niddāyitvā pabuddhakāle tesaṃ santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ kiṃ tumhe‘ nipajjitvā niddāyissāmā’ ti āgatā, sīghaṃ nikkhamitvā samaṇadhammaṃ karothā’’ ti vatvā sayaṃ gantvā tatheva supati. "
594429,122,2522,77,84,1,65,7,Itare majjhimayāme bahi caṅkamitvā pacchimayāme vihāraṃ pavisanti. 
594430,122,2522,85,99,1,96,14,So punapi pabujjhitvā tesaṃ santikaṃ gantvā te vihārā nīharitvā sayaṃ puna gantvā tatheva supati. 
594431,122,2522,100,117,1,121,15,"Tasmiṃ niccakālaṃ evaṃ karonte te bhikkhū sajjhāyaṃ vā kammaṭṭhānaṃ vā manasikātuṃ nāsakkhiṃsu, cittaṃ aññathattaṃ agamāsi. "
594432,122,2522,118,149,1,154,20,"Te‘‘ amhākaṃ ācariyo ativiya āraddhavīriyo, pariggaṇhissāma nan’’ ti pariggaṇhantā tassa kiriyaṃ disvā‘‘ naṭṭhamhā, āvuso, ācariyo no tuccharavaṃ ravatī’’ ti vadiṃsu. "
594433,122,2522,150,158,1,76,8,Tesaṃ ativiya niddāya kilamantānaṃ ekabhikkhupi visesaṃ nibbattetuṃ nāsakkhi. 
594434,122,2522,159,182,1,147,17,"Te vuṭṭhavassā satthu santikaṃ gantvā satthārā katapaṭisanthārā‘‘ kiṃ, bhikkhave, appamattā hutvā samaṇadhammaṃ karitthā’’ ti pucchitā tamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ. "
594435,122,2522,183,201,1,86,11,"Satthā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva, pubbepesa tumhākaṃ antarāyamakāsiyevā’’ ti vatvā tehi yācito–"
