594449,122,2532,2,4,1,28,2,4 . Kumārakassapamātutherīvatthu 
594450,122,2533,2,17,1,114,13,Attā hi attano {nātho}ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto kumārakassapattherassa mātaraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
594451,122,2534,2,11,1,79,9,Sā kira rājagahanagare seṭṭhidhītā viññutaṃ pattakālato paṭṭhāya pabbajjaṃ yāci. 
594452,122,2534,12,28,1,131,15,Atha sā punappunaṃ yācamānāpi mātāpitūnaṃ santikā pabbajjaṃ alabhitvā vayappattā patikulaṃ gantvā patidevatā hutvā agāraṃ ajjhāvasi. 
594453,122,2534,29,35,1,49,6,Athassā na cirasseva kucchismiṃ gabbho patiṭṭhahi. 
594454,122,2534,36,44,1,73,8,Sā gabbhassa patiṭṭhitabhāvaṃ ajānitvāva sāmikaṃ ārādhetvā pabbajjaṃ yāci. 
594455,122,2534,45,57,1,116,12,Atha naṃ so mahantena sakkārena bhikkhunupassayaṃ netvā ajānanto devadattapakkhikānaṃ bhikkhunīnaṃ santike pabbājesi. 
594456,122,2534,58,88,1,130,19,"Aparena samayena bhikkhuniyo tassā gabbhinibhāvaṃ ñatvā tāhi‘‘ kiṃ idan’’ ti vuttā nāhaṃ, ayye, jānāmi‘‘ kimetaṃ’’, sīlaṃ vata me arogamevāti. "
594457,122,2534,89,117,1,166,21,"Bhikkhuniyo taṃ devadattassa santikaṃ netvā‘‘ ayaṃ bhikkhunī saddhāpabbajitā, imissā mayaṃ gabbhassa patiṭṭhitabhāvaṃ jānāma, kālaṃ na jānāma, kiṃ dāni karomā’’ ti pucchiṃsu. "
594458,122,2534,118,140,1,110,14,Devadatto‘‘ mā mayhaṃ ovādakārikānaṃ bhikkhunīnaṃ ayaso uppajjatū’’ ti ettakameva cintetvā‘‘ uppabbājetha nan’’ ti āha. 
594459,122,2534,141,164,1,117,18,"Taṃ sutvā sā daharā mā maṃ, ayye, nāsetha, nāhaṃ devadattaṃ uddissa pabbajitā, etha, maṃ satthu santikaṃ jetavanaṃ nethāti. "
594460,122,2534,165,173,1,45,7,Tā taṃ ādāya jetavanaṃ gantvā satthu ārocesuṃ. 
594461,122,2534,174,197,1,205,19,Satthā‘‘ tassā gihikāle gabbho patiṭṭhito’’ ti jānantopi paravādamocanatthaṃ rājānaṃ pasenadikosalaṃ mahāanāthapiṇḍikaṃ cūḷaanāthapiṇḍikaṃ visākhāupāsikaṃ aññāni ca mahākulāni pakkosāpetvā upālittheraṃ āṇāpesi–
594462,122,2534,198,211,1,73,8,"‘‘ gaccha, imissā daharāya bhikkhuniyā catuparisamajjhe kammaṃ parisodhehī’’ ti. "
594463,122,2534,212,220,1,69,8,Thero rañño purato visākhaṃ pakkosāpetvā taṃ adhikaraṇaṃ paṭicchāpesi. 
594464,122,2534,221,244,1,177,18,Sā sāṇipākāraṃ parikkhipāpetvā antosāṇiyaṃ tassā hatthapādanābhiudarapariyosānāni oloketvā māsadivase samānetvā‘‘ gihibhāve imāya gabbho laddho’’ ti ñatvā therassa tamatthaṃ ārocesi. 
594465,122,2534,245,250,1,56,5,Athassā thero parisamajjhe parisuddhabhāvaṃ patiṭṭhāpesi. 
594466,122,2534,251,260,1,94,9,Sā aparena samayena padumuttarabuddhassa pādamūle patthitapatthanaṃ mahānubhāvaṃ puttaṃ vijāyi. 
594467,122,2535,2,40,1,199,26,"Athekadivasaṃ rājā bhikkhunupassayasamīpena gacchanto dārakasaddaṃ sutvā‘‘ kiṃ idan’’ ti pucchitvā,‘‘ deva, ekissā bhikkhuniyā putto jāto, tassesa saddo’’ ti vutte taṃ kumāraṃ attano gharaṃ netvā dhātīnaṃ adāsi. "
594468,122,2535,41,52,1,101,9,Nāmaggahaṇadivase cassa {kassapo}ti nāmaṃ katvā kumāraparihārena vaḍḍhitattā {kumārakassapo}ti sañjāniṃsu. 
594469,122,2535,53,117,1,276,41,"So kīḷāmaṇḍale dārake paharitvā‘‘ nimmātāpitikenamhā pahaṭā’’ ti vutte rājānaṃ upasaṅkamitvā,‘‘ deva, maṃ‘ nimmātāpitiko’ ti vadanti, mātaraṃ me ācikkhathā’’ ti pucchitvā raññā dhātiyo dassetvā‘‘ imā te mātaro’’ ti vutte‘‘ na ettikā me mātaro, ekāya me mātarā bhavitabbaṃ, taṃ me ācikkhathā’’ ti āha. "
594470,122,2535,118,140,1,99,15,"Rājā‘‘ na sakkā imaṃ vañcetun’’ ti cintetvā, tāta, tava mātā bhikkhunī, tvaṃ mayā bhikkhunupassayā ānītoti. "
