594531,122,2553,2,11,1,43,7,"‘ ‘ Attanā hi kataṃ pāpaṃ, attajaṃ attasambhavaṃ; "
594532,122,2554,2,10,1,49,5,"Abhimatthati dummedhaṃ, vajiraṃvasmamayaṃ maṇin’’ ti. "
594533,122,2555,2,9,1,59,7,Tattha vajiraṃvasmamayaṃ maṇin ti vajiraṃva asmamayaṃ maṇiṃ. 
594534,122,2555,10,50,1,322,36,"Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti– yathā pāsāṇamayaṃ pāsāṇasambhavaṃ vajiraṃ tameva asmamayaṃ maṇiṃ attano uṭṭhānaṭṭhānasaṅkhātaṃ pāsāṇamaṇiṃ khāditvā chiddaṃ chiddaṃ khaṇḍaṃ khaṇḍaṃ katvā aparibhogaṃ karoti, evameva attanā kataṃ attani jātaṃ attasambhavaṃ pāpaṃ dummedhaṃ nippaññaṃ puggalaṃ catūsu apāyesu abhimatthati kantati viddhaṃsetīti. "
