594632,122,2607,2,15,1,98,11,Tassattho – gihibhūtā tāva kākaṇikamattampi attano atthaṃ sahassamattenāpi parassa atthena na hāpaye. 
594633,122,2607,16,27,1,88,10,"Kākaṇikamattenāpi hissa attadatthova khādanīyaṃ vā bhojanīyaṃ vā nipphādeyya, na parattho. "
594634,122,2607,28,55,1,183,21,"Idaṃ pana evaṃ akathetvā kammaṭṭhānasīsena kathitaṃ, tasmā‘‘ attadatthaṃ na hāpemī’’ ti bhikkhunā nāma saṅghassa uppannaṃ cetiyapaṭisaṅkharaṇādikiccaṃ vā upajjhāyādivattaṃ vā na hāpetabbaṃ. "
594635,122,2607,56,64,1,88,7,"Ābhisamācārikavattañhi pūrentoyeva ariyaphalādīni sacchikaroti, tasmā ayampi attadatthova. "
594636,122,2607,65,87,1,139,17,"Yo pana accāraddhavipassako‘‘ ajja vā suve vā’’ ti paṭivedhaṃ patthayamāno vicarati, tena upajjhāyavattādīnipi hāpetvā attano kiccameva kātabbaṃ. "
