594710,122,2634,2,4,1,31,2,3 . Pañcasatavipassakabhikkhuvatthu 
594711,122,2635,2,16,1,108,13,Yathā pubbuḷakan ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto pañcasate vipassake bhikkhū ārabbha kathesi. 
594712,122,2636,2,29,1,205,22,Te kira satthu santike kammaṭṭhānaṃ gahetvā araññaṃ pavisitvā ghaṭentā vāyamantā appavisesā‘‘ visesetvā kammaṭṭhānaṃ gahessāmā’’ ti satthu santikaṃ āgacchantā antarāmagge marīcikammaṭṭhānaṃ bhāventāva āgamiṃsu . 
594713,122,2636,30,35,1,43,5,Tesaṃ vihāraṃ paviṭṭhakkhaṇeyeva devo vassi. 
594714,122,2636,36,58,1,167,18,Te tattha tattha pamukhesu ṭhatvā dhārāvegena uṭṭhahitvā bhijjante pubbaḷake disvā‘‘ ayampi attabhāvo uppajjitvā bhijjanatthena pubbuḷakasadisoyevā’’ ti ārammaṇaṃ gaṇhiṃsu. 
594715,122,2636,59,73,1,109,14,Satthā gandhakuṭiyaṃ nisinnova te bhikkhū oloketvā tehi saddhiṃ kathento viya obhāsaṃ pharitvā imaṃ gāthamāha– 
594716,122,2637,2,4,1,0,0,170.
594717,122,2638,2,11,1,44,7,"‘ ‘ Yathā pubbuḷakaṃ passe, yathā passe marīcikaṃ; "
594718,122,2639,2,12,1,46,7,"Evaṃ lokaṃ avekkhantaṃ, maccurājā na passatī’’ ti. "
594719,122,2640,2,6,1,28,4,Tattha marīcikan ti mayūkhaṃ. 
594720,122,2640,7,16,1,93,9,Te hi dūratova gehasaṇṭhānādivasena upaṭṭhitāpi upagacchantānaṃ agayhūpagā rittakā tucchakāva. 
594721,122,2640,17,34,1,141,14,"Tasmā yathā uppajjitvā bhijjanatthena pubbuḷakaṃ rittatucchādibhāveneva passeyya, evaṃ khandhādilokaṃ avekkhantaṃ maccurājā na {passatī}ti attho. "
594722,122,2641,2,8,1,61,6,Desanāvasāne te bhikkhū ṭhitaṭṭhāneyeva arahattaṃ pāpuṇiṃsūti. 
594723,122,2642,2,4,1,39,2,Pañcasatavipassakabhikkhuvatthu tatiyaṃ.
594724,122,2643,2,4,1,22,2,4 . Abhayarājakumāravatthu 
594725,122,2644,2,14,1,104,12,Etha passathimaṃ lokan ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto abhayarājakumāraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
594726,122,2645,2,18,1,126,14,Tassa kira paccantaṃ vūpasametvā āgatassa pitā bimbisāro tussitvā ekaṃ naccagītakusalaṃ nāṭakitthiṃ datvā sattāhaṃ rajjamadāsi. 
594727,122,2645,19,40,1,179,21,So sattāhaṃ gehā bahi anikkhantova rajjasiriṃ anubhavitvā aṭṭhame divase nadītitthaṃ gantvā nhatvā uyyānaṃ pavisitvā santatimahāmatto viya tassā itthiyā naccagītaṃ passanto nisīdi. 
594728,122,2645,41,49,1,88,8,Sāpi taṅkhaṇaññeva santatimahāmattassa nāṭakitthī viya satthakavātānaṃ vasena kālamakāsi. 
594729,122,2645,50,82,1,162,22,"Kumāro tassā kālakiriyāya uppannasoko‘‘ na me imaṃ sokaṃ ṭhapetvā satthāraṃ añño nibbāpetuṃ sakkhissatī’’ ti satthāraṃ upasaṅkamitvā,‘‘ bhante, sokaṃ me nibbāpethā’’ ti āha. "
594730,122,2645,83,129,1,255,33,"Satthā taṃ samassāsetvā‘‘ tayā hi, kumāra, imissā itthiyā evameva matakāle rodantena pavattitānaṃ assūnaṃ anamatagge saṃsāre pamāṇaṃ natthī’’ ti vatvā tāya desanāya sokassa tanubhāvaṃ ñatvā,‘‘ kumāra, mā soci, bālajanānaṃ saṃsīdanaṭṭhānametan’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
594731,122,2646,2,4,1,0,0,171.
594732,122,2647,2,10,1,44,6,"‘ ‘ Etha passathimaṃ lokaṃ, cittaṃ rājarathūpamaṃ; "
594733,122,2648,2,12,1,47,7,"Yattha bālā visīdanti, natthi saṅgo vijānatan’’ ti. "
594734,122,2649,2,8,1,46,5,Tattha te {passathā}ti rājakumārameva sandhāyāha. 
594735,122,2649,9,15,1,52,6,Imaṃ lokan ti imaṃ khandhalokādisaṅkhātaṃ attabhāvaṃ. 
594736,122,2649,16,22,1,71,6,Cittan ti sattaratanādivicittaṃ rājarathaṃ viya vatthālaṅkārādicittitaṃ. 
594737,122,2649,23,32,1,50,7,Yattha {bālā}ti yasmiṃ attabhāve bālā evaṃ visīdanti. 
594738,122,2649,33,44,1,83,10,Vijānatan ti vijānantānaṃ paṇḍitānaṃ ettha rāgasaṅgādīsu ekopi saṅgo {natthī}ti attho. 
594739,122,2650,2,11,1,93,8,"Desanāvasāne rājakumāro sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi, sampattānampi sātthikā dhammadesanā ahosīti. "
