595080,122,2740,2,4,1,11,2,14 . Buddhavaggo
595081,122,2741,2,4,1,17,2,1 . Māradhītaravatthu 
595082,122,2742,2,16,1,89,11,Yassa jitan ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā bodhimaṇḍe viharanto māradhītaro ārabbha kathesi. 
595083,122,2742,17,25,1,83,8,Desanaṃ pana sāvatthiyaṃ samuṭṭhāpetvā puna kururaṭṭhe māgaṇḍiyabrāhmaṇassa kathesi. 
595084,122,2743,2,10,1,83,8,Kururaṭṭhe kira māgaṇḍiyabrāhmaṇassa dhītā māgaṇḍiyāyeva nāma ahosi uttamarūpadharā. 
595085,122,2743,11,27,1,106,12,Taṃ patthayamānā anekabrāhmaṇamahāsālā ceva khattiyamahāsālā ca‘‘ dhītaraṃ no detū’’ ti māgaṇḍiyassa pahiṇiṃsu. 
595086,122,2743,28,41,1,62,9,Sopi‘‘ na tumhe mayhaṃ dhītu anucchavikā’’ ti sabbe paṭikkhipateva. 
595087,122,2743,42,71,1,215,25,Athekadivasaṃ satthā paccūsasamaye lokaṃ volokento attano ñāṇajālassa anto paviṭṭhaṃ māgaṇḍiyabrāhmaṇaṃ disvā‘‘ kiṃ nu kho bhavissatī’’ ti upadhārento brāhmaṇassa ca brāhmaṇiyā ca tiṇṇaṃ maggaphalānaṃ upanissayaṃ addasa. 
595088,122,2743,72,77,1,46,5,Brāhmaṇopi bahigāme nibaddhaṃ aggiṃ paricarati. 
595089,122,2743,78,84,1,50,6,Satthā pātova pattacīvaramādāya taṃ ṭhānaṃ agamāsi. 
595090,122,2743,85,115,1,162,23,"Brāhmaṇo satthu rūpasiriṃ olokento‘‘ imasmiṃ loke iminā sadiso puriso nāma natthi, ayaṃ mayhaṃ dhītu anucchaviko, imassa me dhītaraṃ dassāmā’’ ti cintetvā satthāraṃ āha–"
595091,122,2743,116,156,1,203,30,"‘‘ samaṇa, mama ekā dhītā atthi, ahaṃ tassā anucchavikaṃ purisaṃ apassanto taṃ na kassaci adāsiṃ, tvaṃ panassā anucchaviko, ahaṃ te dhītaraṃ pādaparicārikaṃ katvā dātukāmo, yāva naṃ ānemi, tāva idheva tiṭṭhāhī’’ ti. "
595092,122,2743,157,166,1,53,8,"Satthā tassa kathaṃ sutvā neva abhinandi, na paṭikkosi. "
595093,122,2744,2,7,1,37,5,Brāhmaṇopi gehaṃ gantvā brāhmaṇiṃ āha–
595094,122,2744,8,33,1,133,19,"‘‘ bhoti, ajja me dhītu anucchaviko puriso diṭṭho, tassa naṃ dassāmā’’ ti dhītaraṃ alaṅkārāpetvā ādāya brāhmaṇiyā saddhiṃ taṃ ṭhānaṃ agamāsi. "
595095,122,2744,34,37,1,32,3,Mahājanopi kutūhalajāto nikkhami. 
