595306,122,2786,69,88,1,118,13,"Titthiyā‘ sattavassikāya tāva sāmaṇeriyā ayamānubhāvo, buddhānubhāvo kīdiso bhavissatī’ ti tumhe adisvāva palāyissantī’’ ti. "
