595694,122,2923,2,21,1,121,15,So kira sāsane pabbajitvā laddhūpasampado‘‘ asukaṭṭhānaṃ nāma gantvā uddesaṃ uggaṇhāhī’’ ti upajjhāyena pesito tattha agamāsi. 
595695,122,2923,22,26,1,27,4,Athassa pituno rogo uppajji. 
595696,122,2923,27,56,1,212,24,So puttaṃ daṭṭhukāmo hutvā taṃ pakkosituṃ samatthaṃ kañci alabhitvā puttasokena vippalapantoyeva āsannamaraṇo hutvā‘‘ idaṃ me puttassa pattacīvaramūlaṃ kareyyāsī’’ ti kahāpaṇasataṃ kaniṭṭhassa hatthe datvā kālamakāsi. 
595697,122,2923,57,88,1,169,23,"So daharassa āgatakāle pādamūle nipatitvā pavaṭṭento roditvā,‘‘ bhante, pitā te vippalapantova kālakato, mayhaṃ pana tena kahāpaṇasataṃ hatthe ṭhapitaṃ, tena kiṃ karomī’’ ti āha. "
595698,122,2923,89,102,1,65,9,Daharo‘‘ na me kahāpaṇehi attho’’ ti paṭikkhipitvā aparabhāge cintesi–
595699,122,2923,103,122,1,99,13,"‘‘ kiṃ me parakulesu piṇḍāya caritvā jīvitena, sakkā taṃ kahāpaṇasataṃ nissāya jīvituṃ, vibbhamissāmī’’ ti. "
595700,122,2923,123,130,1,74,7,So anabhiratiyā pīḷito vissaṭṭhasajjhāyanakammaṭṭhāno paṇḍurogī viya ahosi. 
