595826,122,2958,2,15,1,92,12,Yo {cā}ti idaṃ akhemaṃ anuttamaṃ saraṇaṃ dassetvā khemaṃ uttamaṃ saraṇaṃ dassanatthaṃ āraddhaṃ. 
595827,122,2958,16,49,1,256,27,"Tassattho– yo ca gahaṭṭho vā pabbajito vā‘‘ itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho’’ tiādikaṃ buddhadhammasaṅghānussatikammaṭṭhānaṃ nissāya seṭṭhavasena buddhañca dhammañca saṅghañca saraṇaṃ gato, tassapi taṃ saraṇagamanaṃ aññatitthiyavandanādīhi kuppati calati. "
595828,122,2958,50,63,1,114,12,Tassa pana acalabhāvaṃ dassetuṃ maggena āgatasaraṇameva pakāsanto cattāri ariyasaccāni sammappaññāya {passatī}ti āha. 
595829,122,2958,64,97,1,206,29,"Yo hi etesaṃ saccānaṃ dassanavasena etāni saraṇaṃ gato, etassa etaṃ saraṇaṃ khemañca uttamañca, so ca puggalo etaṃ saraṇaṃ paṭicca sakalasmāpi vaṭṭadukkhā pamuccati, tasmā etaṃ kho saraṇaṃ kheman tiādi vuttaṃ. "
