596589,122,3244,97,110,1,46,8,"Sā,‘‘ bhante, ekova paṭiviso, na sakkā dvidhā kātuṃ. "
596590,122,3244,111,139,1,197,21,"Tumhākaṃ dāsassa idhalokasaṅgahaṃ akatvā paralokasaṅgahaṃ karotha, niravasesameva dātukāmamhī’’ ti vatvā sabbameva therassa patte patiṭṭhapetvā‘‘ tumhehi diṭṭhadhammasseva bhāgī assan’’ ti patthanaṃ akāsi. "
