596826,122,3310,2,4,1,18,2,7 . Atulaupāsakavatthu 
596827,122,3311,2,15,1,96,12,Porāṇametan ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto atulaṃ nāma upāsakaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
596828,122,3312,2,23,1,191,20,So hi sāvatthivāsī upāsako pañcasataupāsakaparivāro ekadivasaṃ te upāsake ādāya dhammassavanatthāya vihāraṃ gantvā revatattherassa santike dhammaṃ sotukāmo hutvā revatattheraṃ vanditvā nisīdi. 
596829,122,3312,24,37,1,82,12,"So panāyasmā paṭisallānārāmo sīho viya ekacāro, tasmā tena saddhiṃ na kiñci kathesi. "
596830,122,3312,38,97,1,304,42,"So‘‘ ayaṃ thero na kiñci kathesī’’ ti kuddho uṭṭhāya sāriputtattherassa santikaṃ gantvā ekamantaṃ ṭhito therena‘‘ kenatthena āgatatthā’’ ti vutte‘‘ ahaṃ, bhante, ime upāsake ādāya dhammassavanatthāya revatattheraṃ upasaṅkamiṃ, tassa me thero na kiñci kathesi, svāhaṃ tassa kujjhitvā idhāgato, dhammaṃ me kathethā’’ ti āha. "
596831,122,3312,98,114,1,84,12,Atha thero‘‘ tena hi upāsakā nisīdathā’’ ti vatvā bahukaṃ katvā abhidhammakathaṃ kathesi. 
596832,122,3312,115,140,1,157,19,"Upāsakopi‘‘ abhidhammakathā nāma atisaṇhā, thero bahuṃ abhidhammameva kathesi, amhākaṃ iminā ko attho’’ ti kujjhitvā parisaṃ ādāya ānandattherassa santikaṃ agamāsi. "
596833,122,3313,2,57,1,318,37,"Therenāpi ‘‘ kiṃ upāsakā’’ ti vutte,‘‘ bhante, mayaṃ dhammassavanatthāya revatattheraṃ upasaṅkamimhā, tassa santike ālāpasallāpamattampi alabhitvā kuddhā sāriputtattherassa santikaṃ agamimhā, sopi no atisaṇhaṃ bahuṃ abhidhammameva kathesi,‘ iminā amhākaṃ ko attho’ ti etassāpi kujjhitvā idhāgamimhā, kathehi no, bhante, dhammakathan’’ ti. "
596834,122,3313,58,70,1,84,11,Tena hi nisīditvā suṇāthāti thero tesaṃ suviññeyyaṃ katvā appakameva dhammaṃ kathesi. 
596835,122,3313,71,85,1,94,13,"Te therassapi kujjhitvā satthu santikaṃ gantvā vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu, atha ne satthā āha–"
596836,122,3313,86,95,1,26,4,‘‘ kasmā upāsakā āgatatthā’’ ti?
596837,122,3313,96,104,1,25,3,"‘‘ Dhammassavanāya, bhante’’ ti."
596838,122,3313,105,114,1,22,5,‘‘ Suto pana vo dhammo’’ ti?
596839,122,3313,115,160,1,286,34,"‘‘ Bhante, mayaṃ ādito revatattheraṃ upasaṅkamimhā, so amhehi saddhiṃ na kiñci kathesi, tassa kujjhitvā sāriputtattheraṃ upasaṅkamimhā, tena no bahu abhidhammo kathito, taṃ asallakkhetvā kujjhitvā ānandattheraṃ upasaṅkamimhā, tena no appamattakova dhammo kathito, tassapi kujjhitvā idhāgatamhā’’ ti. "
596840,122,3314,2,19,1,118,12,"Satthā tassa kathaṃ sutvā,‘‘ atula, porāṇato paṭṭhāya āciṇṇamevetaṃ, tuṇhībhūtampi bahukathampi mandakathampi garahantiyeva. "
596841,122,3314,20,28,1,56,7,Ekantaṃ garahitabboyeva vā hi pasaṃsitabboyeva vā natthi . 
596842,122,3314,29,35,1,42,5,"Rājānopi ekacce nindanti, ekacce pasaṃsanti. "
596843,122,3314,36,49,1,140,12,"Mahāpathavimpi candimasūriyepi ākāsādayopi catuparisamajjhe nisīditvā dhammaṃ kathentampi sammāsambuddhaṃ ekacce garahanti, ekacce pasaṃsanti. "
596844,122,3314,50,76,1,148,22,"Andhabālānañhi nindā vā pasaṃsā vā appamāṇā, paṇḍitena pana medhāvinā nindito nindito nāma, pasaṃsito ca pasaṃsito nāma hotī’’ ti vatvā imā gāthā abhāsi– "
