596887,122,3347,9,18,1,80,8,Kāyena {saṃvuto}ti kāyadvāre duccaritapavesanaṃ nivāretvā saṃvuto pihitadvāro siyā. 
596888,122,3347,19,38,1,131,15,"Yasmā pana kāyaduccaritaṃ hitvā kāyasucaritaṃ caranto ubhayampetaṃ karoti, tasmā kāyaduccaritaṃ hitvā, kāyena sucaritaṃ {care}ti vuttaṃ. "
596889,122,3347,39,42,1,28,3,Anantaragāthāsupi eseva nayo. 
