596895,122,3352,2,4,1,9,2,18 . Malavaggo
596896,122,3353,2,4,1,20,2,1 . Goghātakaputtavatthu 
596897,122,3354,2,17,1,104,11,Paṇḍupalāsova {dānisī}ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ goghātakaputtaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
596898,122,3355,2,21,1,156,18,"Sāvatthiyaṃ kireko goghātako gāvo vadhitvā varamaṃsāni gahetvā pacāpetvā puttadārehi saddhiṃ nisīditvā maṃsañca khādati, mūlena ca vikkiṇitvā jīvikaṃ kappesi. "
596899,122,3355,22,39,1,143,17,So evaṃ pañcapaṇṇāsa vassāni goghātakakammaṃ karonto dhuravihāre viharantassa satthu ekadivasampi kaṭacchumattampi yāguṃ vā bhattaṃ vā na adāsi. 
596900,122,3355,40,47,1,38,7,So ca vinā maṃsena bhattaṃ na bhuñjati. 
596901,122,3355,48,62,1,117,14,So ekadivasaṃ divasabhāge maṃsaṃ vikkiṇitvā attano atthāya pacituṃ ekaṃ maṃsakhaṇḍaṃ bhariyāya datvā nhāyituṃ agamāsi. 
596902,122,3355,63,69,1,42,6,Athassa sahāyako gehaṃ gantvā bhariyaṃ āha–
596903,122,3355,70,85,1,57,9,"‘‘ thokaṃ me vikkiṇiyamaṃsaṃ dehi, gehaṃ me pāhunako āgato’’ ti. "
596904,122,3355,86,96,1,74,9,"Natthi vikkiṇiyamaṃsaṃ, sahāyako te maṃsaṃ vikkiṇitvā idāni nhāyituṃ gatoti. "
596905,122,3355,97,106,1,43,7,"Mā evaṃ kari, sace maṃsakhaṇḍaṃ atthi, dehīti. "
596906,122,3355,107,113,1,54,6,Sahāyakassa te nikkhittamaṃsaṃ ṭhapetvā aññaṃ natthīti. 
596907,122,3355,114,142,1,145,22,"So‘‘ sahāyakassa me atthāya ṭhapitamaṃsato aññaṃ maṃsaṃ natthi, so ca vinā maṃsena na bhuñjati, nāyaṃ dassatī’’ ti sāmaṃyeva taṃ maṃsaṃ gahetvā pakkāmi. "
596908,122,3356,2,20,1,102,14,Goghātakopi nhatvā āgato tāya attano pakkapaṇṇena saddhiṃ vaḍḍhetvā bhatte upanīte āha‘‘ kahaṃ maṃsan’’ ti?
596909,122,3356,21,29,1,14,3,"‘‘ Natthi, sāmī’’ ti. "
596910,122,3356,30,36,1,43,6,Nanu ahaṃ paccanatthāya maṃsaṃ datvā gatoti. 
596911,122,3356,37,78,1,214,31,"Tava sahāyako āgantvā‘‘ pāhunako me āgato, vikkiṇiyamaṃsaṃ dehī’’ ti vatvā mayā‘‘ sahāyakassa te ṭhapitamaṃsato aññaṃ maṃsaṃ natthi, so ca vinā maṃsena na bhuñjatī’’ ti vuttepi balakkārena taṃ maṃsaṃ sāmaṃyeva gahetvā gatoti. "
596912,122,3356,79,88,1,50,8,"Ahaṃ vinā maṃsena bhattaṃ na bhuñjāmi, harāhi nanti. "
596913,122,3356,89,96,1,29,5,"Kiṃ sakkā kātuṃ, bhuñja, sāmīti. "
596914,122,3356,97,142,1,297,38,"So‘‘ nāhaṃ bhuñjāmī’’ ti taṃ bhattaṃ harāpetvā satthaṃ ādāya pacchāgehe ṭhito goṇo atthi, tassa santikaṃ gantvā mukhe hatthaṃ pakkhipitvā jivhaṃ nīharitvā satthena mūle chinditvā ādāya gantvā aṅgāresu pacāpetvā bhattamatthake ṭhapetvā nisinno ekaṃ bhattapiṇḍaṃ bhuñjitvā ekaṃ maṃsakhaṇḍaṃ mukhe ṭhapesi. "
596915,122,3356,143,149,1,51,5,Taṅkhaṇaññevassa jivhā chijjitvā bhattapātiyaṃ pati. 
596916,122,3356,150,154,1,44,4,Taṅkhaṇaññeva kammasarikkhakaṃ vipākaṃ labhi. 
