596988,122,3387,38,107,1,445,54,"Tadāpi brāhmaṇo bhikkhū olokentova ṭhito tintacīvarake bhikkhū disvā‘‘ ettha mayā sālaṃ kāretuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti sālaṃ kāretvā‘‘ idāni sālamahaṃ karissāmī’’ ti cintetvā buddhappamukhaṃ bhikkhusaṅghaṃ nimantetvā anto ca bahi ca bhikkhū nisīdāpetvā bhattakiccāvasāne anumodanatthāya satthu pattaṃ gahetvā,‘‘ bhante, ahaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ cīvarapārupanakāle imasmiṃ ṭhāne olokento ṭhito idañcidañca disvā idañcidañca kāresin’’ ti ādito paṭṭhāya sabbaṃ taṃ pavattiṃ ārocesi. "
