597152,122,3457,2,10,1,67,7,"Tesu hi eko pāṇātipātāveramaṇisikkhāpadameva rakkhati, itare itarāni. "
597153,122,3457,11,32,1,118,15,"Te ekadivasaṃ‘‘ ahaṃ dukkaraṃ karomi, dukkaraṃ rakkhāmī’’ ti vivādāpannā satthu santikaṃ gantvā vanditvā tamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ. "
