597164,122,3467,2,14,1,108,11,Tattha yo {pāṇamatipātetī}ti yo sāhatthikādīsu chasu payogesu ekapayogenāpi parassa jīvitindriyaṃ upacchindati. 
597165,122,3467,15,21,1,57,6,Musāvādan ti paresaṃ atthabhañjanakaṃ musāvādañca bhāsati. 
597166,122,3467,22,32,1,99,9,Loke {adinnamādiyatī}ti imasmiṃ sattaloke theyyāvahārādīsu ekenapi avahārena parapariggahitaṃ ādiyati. 
597167,122,3467,33,42,1,89,8,Paradārañca {gacchatī}ti parassa rakkhitagopitesu bhaṇḍesu aparajjhanto uppathacāraṃ carati. 
