598101,122,3837,24,35,1,127,10,"Sabbattha jaṇṇuppamāṇaūruppamāṇakaṭippamāṇādīni udakāni sandantāni sabbakuṇapāni gaṅgaṃ pavesayiṃsu, parisuddho bhūmibhāgo ahosi. "
598102,122,3837,36,51,1,116,14,Licchavīrājāno satthāraṃ yojane yojane vasāpetvā mahādānaṃ datvā diguṇaṃ pūjaṃ karontā tīhi divasehi vesāliṃ nayiṃsu. 
598103,122,3837,52,63,1,103,10,"Sakko devarājā devagaṇaparivuto āgamāsi, mahesakkhānaṃ devānaṃ sannipātena amanussā yebhuyyena palāyiṃsu. "
598104,122,3837,64,70,1,54,6,Satthā sāyaṃ nagaradvāre ṭhatvā ānandattheraṃ āmantesi–
598105,122,3837,71,91,1,122,14,"‘‘ imaṃ, ānanda, ratanasuttaṃ uggaṇhitvā licchavīkumārehi saddhiṃ vicaranto vesāliyā tiṇṇaṃ pākārānaṃ antare parittaṃ karohī’’ ti. "
598106,122,3838,2,53,1,561,50,Thero satthārā dinnaṃ ratanasuttaṃ uggaṇhitvā satthu selamayapattena udakaṃ ādāya nagaradvāre ṭhito paṇidhānato paṭṭhāya tathāgatassa dasa pāramiyo dasa upapāramiyo dasa paramatthapāramiyoti samatiṃsa pāramiyo pañca mahāpariccāge lokatthacariyā ñātatthacariyā buddhatthacariyāti tisso cariyāyo pacchimabhave gabbhavokkantiṃ jātiṃ abhinikkhamanaṃ padhānacariyaṃ bodhipallaṅke māravijayaṃ sabbaññutaññāṇapaṭivedhaṃ dhammacakkapavattanaṃ navalokuttaradhammeti sabbepime buddhaguṇe āvajjetvā nagaraṃ pavisitvā tiyāmarattiṃ tīsu pākārantaresu parittaṃ karonto vicari. 
598107,122,3838,54,67,1,74,9,Tena‘‘ yaṃkiñcī’’ ti vuttamatteyeva uddhaṃ khittaudakaṃ amanussānaṃ upari pati.
598108,122,3838,68,85,1,122,13,‘‘ Yānīdha bhūtānī’’ ti gāthākathanato paṭṭhāya rajatavaṭaṃsakā viya udakabindūni ākāsena gantvā gilānamanussānaṃ upari patiṃsu. 
598109,122,3838,86,93,1,63,6,Tāvadeva vūpasantarogā manussā uṭṭhāyuṭṭhāya theraṃ parivāresuṃ .
598110,122,3838,94,113,1,154,15,‘‘ Yaṃkiñcī’’ ti vuttapadato paṭṭhāya pana udakaphusitehi phuṭṭhaphuṭṭhā sabbe apalāyantā saṅkārakūṭabhittipadesādinissitā amanussā tena tena dvārena palāyiṃsu. 
598111,122,3838,114,117,1,24,3,Dvārāni anokāsāni ahesuṃ. 
598112,122,3838,118,124,1,49,6,Te okāsaṃ alabhantā pākāraṃ bhinditvāpi palāyiṃsu. 
598113,122,3839,2,15,1,146,13,Mahājano nagaramajjhe santhāgāraṃ sabbagandhehi upalimpetvā upari suvaṇṇatārakādivicittaṃ vitānaṃ bandhitvā buddhāsanaṃ paññāpetvā satthāraṃ ānesi. 
598114,122,3839,16,20,1,28,4,Satthā paññatte āsane nisīdi. 
