598120,122,3839,59,72,1,134,13,Evaṃ punadivasepīti sattāhaṃ tadeva ratanasuttaṃ desetvā sabbabhayānaṃ vūpasantabhāvaṃ ñatvā licchavīgaṇaṃ āmantetvā vesālito nikkhami. 
598121,122,3839,73,83,1,87,10,Licchavīrājāno diguṇaṃ sakkāraṃ karontā puna tīhi divasehi satthāraṃ gaṅgātīraṃ nayiṃsu. 
598122,122,3840,2,5,1,35,3,Gaṅgāya nibbattanāgarājāno cintesuṃ–
598123,122,3840,6,21,1,60,9,"‘‘ manussā tathāgatassa sakkāraṃ karonti, mayaṃ kiṃ na karomā’’ ti. "
598124,122,3840,22,49,1,216,21,"Te suvaṇṇarajatamaṇimayā nāvāyo māpetvā suvaṇṇarajatamaṇimaye pallaṅke paññāpetvā pañcavaṇṇapadumasañchannaṃ udakaṃ karitvā,‘‘ bhante, amhākampi anuggahaṃ karothā’’ ti attano attano nāvaṃ abhiruhaṇatthāya satthāraṃ yāciṃsu."
