598132,122,3841,15,32,1,172,17,Satthā gaṅgāya ubhosu passesu rājūnaṃ mahantaṃ pariccāgaṃ oloketvā nāgādīnañca ajjhāsayaṃ viditvā ekekāya nāvāya pañcapañcabhikkhusataparivāraṃ ekekaṃ nimmitabuddhaṃ māpesi. 
