598174,122,3848,2,12,1,43,6,"‘ ‘ Mattāsukhapariccāgā , passe ce vipulaṃ sukhaṃ; "
598175,122,3849,2,12,1,50,7,"Caje mattāsukhaṃ dhīro, sampassaṃ vipulaṃ sukhan’’ ti. "
598176,122,3850,2,13,1,98,9,"Tattha {mattāsukhapariccāgā}ti mattāsukhan ti pamāṇayuttakaṃ parittasukhaṃ vuccati, tassa pariccāgena. "
598177,122,3850,14,26,1,77,11,"Vipulaṃ sukhan ti uḷāraṃ sukhaṃ nibbānasukhaṃ vuccati, taṃ ce passeyyāti attho. "
598178,122,3850,27,53,1,198,24,"Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti– ekañhi bhojanapātiṃ sajjāpetvā bhuñjantassa mattāsukhaṃ nāma uppajjati, taṃ pana pariccajitvā uposathaṃ vā karontassa dānaṃ vā dadantassa vipulaṃ uḷāraṃ nibbānasukhaṃ nāma nibbattati. "
598179,122,3850,54,73,1,140,18,"Tasmā sace evaṃ tassa mattāsukhassa pariccāgā vipulaṃ sukhaṃ passati, athetaṃ vipulaṃ sukhaṃ sammā passanto paṇḍito taṃ mattāsukhaṃ cajeyyāti. "
