598617,122,4056,2,11,1,70,9,Te kira ekasmiṃ paccante vassaṃ upagantvā paṭhamamāse sukhaṃ vihariṃsu. 
598618,122,4056,12,21,1,79,9,Majjhimamāse corā āgantvā tesaṃ gocaragāmaṃ paharitvā karamare gahetvā agamaṃsu. 
598619,122,4056,22,37,1,133,15,Tato paṭṭhāya manussā corānaṃ paṭibāhanatthāya taṃ paccantanagaraṃ abhisaṅkharontā te bhikkhū sakkaccaṃ upaṭṭhātuṃ okāsaṃ na labhiṃsu. 
