598622,122,4056,96,136,1,217,29,"Tasmā aphāsukaṃ vassaṃ vasimhā’’ ti vutte‘‘ alaṃ, bhikkhave, mā cintayittha, phāsuvihāro nāma niccakālaṃ dullabho, bhikkhunā nāma yathā te manussā nagaraṃ gopayiṃsu, evaṃ attabhāvameva gopayituṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
