598644,122,4073,2,6,1,33,3,Tattha {alajjitāye}ti alajjitabbena. 
598645,122,4073,7,19,1,90,11,"Bhikkhābhājanañhi alajjitabbaṃ nāma, te pana taṃ paṭicchādetvā vicarantā tena lajjanti nāma. "
598646,122,4073,20,25,1,55,4,{Lajjitāye}ti apaṭicchannena hirikopīnaṅgena lajjitabbena. 
598647,122,4073,26,36,1,63,9,Te pana taṃ apaṭicchādetvā vicarantā lajjitāye na lajjanti nāma. 
598648,122,4073,37,50,1,121,12,Tena tesaṃ alajjitabbena lajjitaṃ lajjitabbena alajjitaṃ tucchagahaṇabhāvena ca aññathāgahaṇabhāvena ca micchādiṭṭhi hoti. 
598649,122,4073,51,62,1,102,11,Taṃ samādiyitvā vicarantā pana te micchādiṭṭhisamādānā sattā nirayādibhedaṃ duggatiṃ gacchantīti attho. 
598650,122,4073,63,80,1,177,15,"{Abhaye}ti bhikkhābhājanaṃ nissāya rāgadosamohamānadiṭṭhikilesaduccaritabhayānaṃ anuppajjanato bhikkhābhājanaṃ abhayaṃ nāma, bhayena taṃ paṭicchādentā pana abhaye bhayadassino nāma. "
598651,122,4073,81,94,1,108,12,"Hirikopīnaṅgaṃ pana nissāya rāgādīnaṃ uppajjanato taṃ bhayaṃ nāma, tassa apaṭicchādanena bhaye cābhayadassino. "
598652,122,4073,95,104,1,92,9,Tassa taṃ ayathāgahaṇassa samādinnattā micchādiṭṭhisamādānā sattā duggahiṃ gacchantīti attho. 
598653,122,4074,2,12,1,96,9,"Desanāvasāne bahū nigaṇṭhā saṃviggamānasā pabbajiṃsu, sampattānampi sātthikā dhammadesanā ahosīti. "
598654,122,4075,2,4,1,23,2,Nigaṇṭhavatthu aṭṭhamaṃ.
598655,122,4076,2,4,1,20,2,9 . Titthiyasāvakavatthu 
598656,122,4077,2,14,1,84,9,{Avajje}ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto titthiyasāvake ārabbha kathesi. 
598657,122,4078,2,33,1,225,26,"Ekasmiñhi samaye aññatitthiyasāvakā attano putte sammādiṭṭhikānaṃ upāsakānaṃ puttehi saddhiṃ saparivāre kīḷamāne disvā gehaṃ āgatakāle‘‘ na vo samaṇā sakyaputtiyā vanditabbā, nāpi tesaṃ vihāraṃ pavisitabban’’ ti sapathaṃ kārayiṃsu. "
598658,122,4078,34,41,1,80,7,Te ekadivasaṃ jetavanavihārassa bahidvārakoṭṭhakasāmante kīḷantā pipāsitā ahesuṃ. 
598659,122,4078,42,57,1,87,11,Athekaṃ upāsakadārakaṃ‘‘ tvaṃ ettha gantvā pānīyaṃ pivitvā amhākampi āharāhī’’ ti pahiṇiṃsu. 
