599221,122,4335,2,35,1,300,32,Imaṃ pana desanaṃ sutvā so rājapurisānaṃ antare sūlagge nisinnova udayabbayaṃ paṭṭhapetvā tilakkhaṇaṃ āropetvā saṅkhāre sammasanto sotāpattiphalaṃ patvā samāpattisukhaṃ anubhavanto vehāsaṃ uppatitvā ākāseneva satthu santikaṃ gantvā satthāraṃ vanditvā sarājikāya parisāya majjheyeva arahattaṃ pāpuṇīti. 
