599223,122,4337,2,4,1,18,2,4 . Bandhanāgāravatthu 
599224,122,4338,2,15,1,91,12,Na taṃ daḷhan ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto bandhanāgāraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
599225,122,4339,2,12,1,99,9,Ekasmiṃ kira kāle bahū sandhicchedakapanthaghātakamanussaghātake core ānetvā kosalarañño dassayiṃsu. 
599226,122,4339,13,17,1,64,4,Te rājā andubandhanarajjubandhanasaṅkhalikabandhanehi bandhāpesi. 
599227,122,4339,18,82,1,455,54,"Tiṃsamattāpi kho jānapadā bhikkhū satthāraṃ daṭṭhukāmā āgantvā disvā vanditvā punadivase sāvatthiṃ piṇḍāya carantā bandhanāgāraṃ gantvā te core disvā piṇḍapātapaṭikkantā sāyanhasamaye tathāgataṃ upasaṅkamitvā,‘‘ bhante, ajja amhehi piṇḍāya carantehi bandhanāgāre bahū corā andubandhanādīhi baddhā mahādukkhaṃ anubhavantā diṭṭhā, te tāni bandhanāni chinditvā palāyituṃ na sakkonti, atthi nu kho, bhante, tehi bandhanehi thirataraṃ aññaṃ bandhanaṃ nāmā’’ ti pucchiṃsu. "
599228,122,4339,83,122,1,302,30,"Satthā,‘‘ bhikkhave, kiṃ bandhanāni nāmetāni, yaṃ panetaṃ dhanadhaññaputtadārādīsu taṇhāsaṅkhātaṃ kilesabandhanaṃ, etaṃ etehi sataguṇena sahassaguṇena satasahassaguṇena thirataraṃ, evaṃ mahantampi panetaṃ ducchindaniyaṃ bandhanaṃ porāṇakapaṇḍitā chinditvā himavantaṃ pavisitvā pabbajiṃsū’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari– "
599229,122,4340,2,11,1,92,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto ekasmiṃ duggatagahapatikule nibbatti. 
599230,122,4340,12,16,1,35,4,Tassa vayappattassa pitā kālamakāsi. 
599231,122,4340,17,22,1,30,5,So bhatiṃ katvā mātaraṃ posesi. 
599232,122,4340,23,32,1,80,9,Athassa mātā anicchamānasseva ekaṃ kuladhītaraṃ gehe katvā aparabhāge kālamakāsi. 
599233,122,4340,33,37,1,42,4,Bhariyāyapissa kucchiyaṃ gabbho patiṭṭhahi. 
599234,122,4340,38,58,1,95,13,"So gabbhassa patiṭṭhitabhāvaṃ ajānantova,‘‘ bhadde, tvaṃ bhatiṃ katvā jīva, ahaṃ pabbajissāmī’’ ti āha."
599235,122,4340,59,78,1,78,12,"‘‘ Sāmi, nanu gabbho me patiṭṭhito, mayi vijātāya dārakaṃ disvā pabbajissasī’’ ti āha. "
599236,122,4340,79,105,1,106,15,"So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā tassā vijātakāle,‘‘ bhadde, tvaṃ sotthinā vijātā, idāni ahaṃ pabbajissāmī’’ ti āpucchi. "
599237,122,4340,106,124,1,88,13,Atha naṃ sā‘‘ puttassa tāva thanapānato apagamanakālaṃ āgamehī’’ ti vatvā puna gabbhaṃ gaṇhi. 
599238,122,4340,125,127,1,10,2,So cintesi–
599239,122,4340,128,143,1,85,10,"‘‘ imaṃ sampaṭicchāpetvā gantuṃ na sakkā, imissā anācikkhitvāva palāyitvā pabbajissāmī’’ ti. "
599240,122,4340,144,151,1,49,6,So tassā anācikkhitvāva rattibhāge uṭṭhāya palāyi. 
