599354,122,4391,2,28,1,225,22,Atīte kira kassapadasabalassa suvaṇṇacetiye kariyamāne bārāṇasivāsino kulaputtā bahuṃ khādanīyabhojanīyaṃ yānakesu āropetvā‘‘ hatthakammaṃ karissāmā’’ ti cetiyaṭṭhānaṃ gacchantā antarāmagge ekaṃ theraṃ piṇḍāya pavisantaṃ passiṃsu. 
